 irely by hand\, learning looping and shaping techniques along the way. Mis
 takes are welcome—we’ll show you how to fix them with ease.\nWhat’s 
 Included:\n• Luxurious neutral-toned and colourful chunky chenille yarn\
 n• Step-by-step instruction from an experienced instructor\n• All mate
 rials and supplies provided\n• Complimentary snacks\, coffee\, and refre
 shments\nBy the end of the workshop\, you’ll take home your own cozy\, h
 andmade blanket—perfect to use or gift.\nWho Can Attend:\nIdeal for begi
 nners and anyone seeking a calming\, hands-on creative experience. Ages 8+
  welcome. Guests under 16 must attend with a paying adult.\nNo experience 
 needed!\nSee more events at: https://www.artboxstudiogallery.com/calendar\
 nCall us at: 647-617-9550
