 g Workshop and create a one-of-a-kind fluid art piece that can never be re
 created.\nEnjoy our vibrant 2-level gallery\, enjoy snacks\, coffee/tea\, 
 before diving into the mesmerizing experience of glowing paint pouring. Le
 arn essential techniques such as flip cup\, paint blowing\, and intentiona
 l pours\, along with colour mixing and flow methods—all guided by our in
 structor.\nDuration:\n• Approx. 1.5- 2 hours (depending on quantity of p
 roject choices)\nWhat’s Included:\n• Project choices include an 11x14
 ” stretched canvas and/or white fluid bear\, KAWS Figurine and fluid key
 chain.\n• Glow-in-the-dark\, neon and acrylic paints\, pouring mediums\,
  glitter\, gold/silver leaf\n• Apron and all supplies\n• Snacks\, coff
 ee\, tea\, and refreshments\nYour artwork is welcome to stay to dry safely
  or can be packed to-go\, same day. Your art will fully dry within 24 hour
 s.\nWho Can Attend:\nOpen to beginners and experienced artists alike. Ages
