BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Ballets Jazz Montreal: Dance Me - Music by Leonard Cohen
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260411T200000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260411T230000
UID:blogto-230883@blogto.com
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://blogto-production2-baselayer-display.blo
 gto.com/events/2026/02/14/original_image78f1ae29-aebd-4634-a8cd-5e9b5d5d45
 7d.jpg
DESCRIPTION:A breathtaking tribute to Leonard Cohen\, where powerhouse dan
 cers bring his legendary music and poetry to life through bold\, unforgett
 able choreography.\n“The show is more than an illustration\, more than a
 n evocation. It allows us to internally revisit the notion of the human be
 ing and human existence\, a vision of the five stages of life\, all at onc
 e sensual\, sensitive\, carnal\, and mystical\, which is the watermark of 
 Leonard Cohen’s work and explains the singularity of his impact.” —L
 e Métropole\, Montréal\nDance Me - Music by Leonard Cohen is an exclusiv
 e creation inspired by the rich and profound work of Montréal-based poet\
 , artist\, and songwriter\, Leonard Cohen.\nApproved by Cohen during his l
 ifetime\, this riveting homage to the famed artist evokes the grand cycles
  of existence\, as described in Cohen’s deeply reflective music and poem
 s.\nThree internationally renowned choreographers were entrusted with putt
 ing movement to Cohen’s legendary songs: Andonis Foniadakis\, Annabelle 
 Lopez Ochoa\, and Ihsan Rustem. Their powerful and profound choreographic 
 world\, reflective of Cohen’s singular work\, is brought to life by Ball
 ets Jazz Montréal’s 14 artists and the strong\, bold dramaturgy of Eric
  Jean.\nSurrounded by a team of celebrated designers\, Dance Me combines s
 cenic\, visual\, musical\, dramaturgical\, and choreographic writing to pa
 y tribute to Montréal’s greatest ambassador. Dance\, music\, lighting\,
  scenography\, and videography all come together in this unforgettable sho
 w.\nTickets available @ https://eventschaser.com/?s=Music+by+Leonard+Cohen
 +Toronto
LOCATION:Meridian Hall
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/ballets-jazz-montreal-dance-me-music-by-
 leonard-cohen-toronto-2/
X-SOURCE:blogTO
END:VEVENT
