 gto.com/events/2026/03/29/original_image288b14a6-0adb-4041-9e08-09ae368ca2
 46.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an exclusive dining experience for couples looking
  meet like-minded couples for friendship.\nJoin The Social Couple for a "p
 roduction-meets-dining" experience at Spaccio East. This unique Corktown g
 em serves as the high-energy heart of the Terroni empire\, where a rustic-
 industrial vibe meets world-class craftsmanship. Our small dinner party wi
 ll gather in an open-concept space suspended above a massive 16\,000-squar
 e-foot production hub\, offering a front-row seat to the "culinary show" o
 f master bakers and pasta makers.\nThe menu is a vibrant celebration of It
 alian soul\, featuring handmade pasta crafted from scratch\, freshly baked
  artisanal breads\, and authentic Sud Forno pastries. To complement the me
 al\, you can indulge in expertly shaken Italian cocktails\, a curated sele
 ction of fine wines\, or a classic espresso from the cafe. It’s an eveni
 ng where the grit of a commercial factory meets the elegance of a high-end
  trattoria\, creating the perfect\, flamboyant backdrop.\nTickets to this 
 exclusive dinner party are limited\, and on a first-come\, first-served ba
 sis. Your ticket includes your event entry\, access to this one-of-a-kind 
 venue\, and a unique opportunity to meet and build friendships with other 
 like-minded couples in the city.\nRSVP Today! Secure your spot now for an 
 unforgettable night of food\, flair\, and friendship.
LOCATION:Spaccio East
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/couples-dining-in-corktown-16000-sq-ft-o
 f-culinary-art-toronto/
