BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Nagata Shachu X Ryunosuke Yamazumi Rhythms in Flight
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260411T200000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260411T213000
UID:blogto-229535@blogto.com
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://blogto-production2-baselayer-display.blo
 gto.com/events/2026/01/21/original_imageaee3533a-609e-47ab-8b5f-7d2d4e7eaf
 57.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Nagata Shachu will close their 28th season with Nagata Shachu 
 X Ryunosuke Yamazumi: Rhythms in Flight on April 11\, 2026 at The Fleck at
  Harbourfront Centre Theatre. This performance and collaboration will feat
 ure the energy\, discipline and passion of both taiko and circus\, perform
 ed by extraordinary and renowned Japanese artists from each art form.\nNag
 ata Shachu will create two new works to accompany Ryunosuke's signature ci
 rcus acts\, and Ryunosuke\, who is also a musician\, will perform a drummi
 ng piece with Nagata Shachu. Ryunosuke will perform his signature routines
  with breathtaking acrobatic precision on a free-standing pole over 10 fee
 t in the air. Using a Chinese pole and balls\, he explores the limits of h
 is body\, free from all gravity.
