DESCRIPTION:This is your captain\, Kid Artik\, speaking live from the brid
 ge! We've lifted anchor and have set sail for the first Patio Lanterns of 
 2026. So join the Yachtly Crew as we celebrate all the Aries (and The Capt
 ain's) birthdays with the best people and music ever! Smooth Yacht Rock\, 
 AM Gold\, and timeless Soul Classics.\nPicture the glow off a vintage ster
 eo\, record crackles and static from a dusty needle\, late night FM radio\
 , and those long drives where the perfect song finds you at exactly the ri
 ght moment in time. That's Patio Lanterns!\nThink of the perfect Yacht Roc
 k\, Soft Rock\, AOR (adult-oriented rock) music you love\, like Steely Dan
 \, Michael McDonald\, Ambrosia\, and America. Now mix in some breezy AM Go
 ld grooves by Nicolette Larson\, Anne Murray\, Toto\, Christopher Cross\, 
 and The Doobie Brothers. To classic Soulful harmonies like the timeless mu
 sic from George Benson\, Earth\, Wind & Fire\, Anita Baker to Kool & The G
 ang\, Chaka Khan\, and Sade.\nThis is the third space you've been looking 
 for. Expect an evening full of great people who know every lyric\, who sin
 g without hesitation\, and who understand the joy and shared love for the 
 classics that never gets old!\nTickets and space are limited!! https://www
 .eventbrite.ca/e/patio-lanterns-yacht-rock-am-gold-and-soul-classics-ticke
 ts-1984847069014\nSo get your Hawaiian shirts\, sundresses\, favourite ban
 d shirts\, nautical gear or anything that yodels "Yacht Rock attire" for P
 atio Lanterns - Kid Artik's Aries Birthday Bash!\nYou know what to do\, si
 ng it with me now... "Those Patio Lanterns\, they were the stars in our sk
 y\, Those patio lanterns\, lighting up our lives. Oh those Patio Lanterns.
 .."
LOCATION:Roses New York
