 't get in\, the pub crawl is not responsible for you!\n➡️ Every bar/cl
 ub we are going to is less than 5 mins walking from the next one. So don
 ’t worry about needing to walk any sort of long distance.\n➡️ Make s
 ure to come early so you can socialize with the group before things get cr
 azy!\nGET YOUR TICKETS HERE- https://pubcrawltoronto.com/book-now/
