  Using pre-made sushi rice\, participants will then roll up their sleeves 
 and create their own maki rolls from start to finish. You’ll practice si
 mple knife skills by cutting your own cucumber\, learn how to roll sushi u
 sing traditional techniques\, and slice your finished rolls to enjoy! Best
  of all\, this event supports a great cause. All proceeds from the worksho
 p will be donated to the Bluffs Food Bank. Come learn a new skill\, have f
 un\, and help support the community!\nRegister Online to secure your spot.
 \nLocation: 200 McIntosh St\, Scarborough\, ON M1N 3Z3 (nearest TTC subway
