 m-2:45pm\nTime Slots: 4 time slots\nDuration: 1 hour each--> 10am-11am\, 1
 1:15am-12:15pm\, 12:30pm-1:30pm\, 1:45pm- 2:45pm\nCapacity PER time slot: 
 20 participants\nAges: 6+\nCost: $20+HST/ participant ****All Proceeds wil
