BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Shrine to Yourself: A Self-Worship Zine Party
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260411T130000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260411T143000
UID:blogto-233340@blogto.com
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://blogto-production2-baselayer-display.blo
 gto.com/events/2026/04/08/original_image87e9a83d-602a-439a-a9ac-474532d300
 c7.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Make a tiny zine shrine to yourself! A playful\, heartfelt wor
 kshop with creative prompts\, sweet vibes\, and room for all your feelings
 !\nGet in\, babe — we’re making zines and it’s all about you! Join u
 s for a sweet\, reflective\, and silly day of zine-making at Loohoo. No ex
 perience necessary — we’ll hang out\, cut things up\, glue things down
 \, and make little shrines to ourselves — the weird\, lovely\, tired\, g
 lowing\, trying versions of us.\nYou’ll get a lovingly crafted list of p
 rompts to choose from — whether you’re in the mood to reflect deeply (
 “A pep talk from future me\,” “Things I release / things I call in
 ”)\, or something more playful and visual (“Draw your aura\,” “If 
 I were an inanimate object…”). There’s no wrong way to do this.\nBri
 ng a friend or come solo. Flirt with yourself on paper. Let it be a gift t
 o you!\n💌 What’s Included:\nOne-sheet zine folding instructions (it
 ’s easy & fun!)\nA whole menu of creative\, tender prompts\nPens\, sciss
 ors\, markers\, collage material\, glue\nA cozy vibe + a welcoming space\n
 You’ll leave with a tiny handmade zine: part time capsule\, part love le
 tter to yourself\, part magic spell 🌙📓🖍️💫✂️✨ No art sk
 ills required!\nYou’re also welcome to browse Loohoo during the workshop
 ! It's like a little museum of cuteness\, and every little purchase helps 
 keep the magic going ✨\n✨ About the Facilitator\nHi! I’m Lindsay\, c
 ute shop owner of Loohoo\, and I’ll be facilitating this workshop myself
 ! Loohoo is my dreamy little shop in Parkdale\, and I feel so grateful to 
 be hosting creative\, heartfelt events like this. I believe in making spac
 e for playing\, softness\, small joys\, and feelings. I think this night w
 ill be beautiful\, goofy\, and maybe a little emotional\, crying is allowe
 d!!💗\nShrine to Yourself — A Self-Worship Zine Party\n📍 Loohoo 138
 0 Queen St W Toronto\n🎟️ Tickets – Pay What You Can! Pay what feels
  good for your heart + wallet!\n💫 About Loohoo\nLoohoo is a cozy gift a
 nd lifestyle shop in Parkdale\, designed to feel like a dreamy apartment 
 — playful\, colourful\, and full of charm. Think: cute stuff for cute pe
 ople\, curated with whimsy.\nWe host fun events like crafty workshops\, cu
 te pop-ups\, and mini themed markets to bring our community together and c
 elebrate local makers. Whether you’re crafting\, shopping\, or just popp
 ing in for good energy\, Loohoo is your new favourite cute shop!\n💕 Fol
 low along on Instagram @shop.loohoo to see what new things are happening a
 t the shop!
LOCATION:Loohoo
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/shrine-to-yourself-a-self-worship-zine-p
 arty-toronto/
X-SOURCE:blogTO
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
