 73.jpg
DESCRIPTION:SoFresh4Dem is a community social experience created for the e
 nergy\, culture\, and diversity that define Toronto and the GTA. Produced 
 by Fresheyed Production\, this event brings together creatives\, entrepren
 eurs\, young professionals\, artists\, and culture lovers for an evening b
 uilt around genuine connection and shared experiences.\nRooted in Toronto
 ’s multicultural spirit\, SoFresh4Dem creates a welcoming space where pe
 ople from different backgrounds can meet naturally\, discover local busine
 sses\, and engage with a growing creative community. The focus is simple: 
 real conversations\, authentic connections\, and an atmosphere that feels 
 both vibrant and inclusive.\nWhether you are coming from downtown Toronto\
 , Scarborough\, Brampton\, Mississauga\, North York\, or surrounding areas
 \, this event serves as a meeting point for people who value creativity\, 
 community\, and culture.\nWhat to Expect\nLocal GTA vendors and emerging b
 rands\nMusic and karaoke experiences\nFood\, drinks\, and a vibrant social
  atmosphere\nCreative networking and community connection\nOpportunities t
 o discover and support local talent\nSoFresh4Dem is not about crowded nigh
 tlife. It is about meaningful moments\, new connections\, and creating spa
 ce for community to grow offline.\nEvent Details\nDate April 11\nTime 6:00
  PM to 9:00 PM\nLocation TacoTaco Bar\, Kensington Market\, Toronto\nJoin 
 us for an evening that celebrates Toronto’s cultural identity while brin
 ging people together through creativity\, collaboration\, and shared energ
 y.\nHosted by Fresheyed Production\, a creative production and event compa
 ny dedicated to building culture through community.
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/sofresh4dem-toronto/
X-SOURCE:blogTO
END:VEVENT
