DESCRIPTION:Join us at a unique Candle Making Experience at Artbox\nWhat t
 o Expect:\nExperience an aromatic soy candle crafting workshop where you'l
 l learn step by step how to make two personalized candles and a surprise m
 ini gift. Mix & match your scents\, colours and decor. You'll also have th
 e option to paint your glass vessels to create your own unique candles to 
 take home same day.\nIntroduction to Candle Making: Our experienced chandl
 er will teach you all the basics of candle making\, including the benefits
  of using soy wax\, and the step-by-step process to create beautiful custo
 m candles.\nChoose Your Scent: Select from a variety of delightful\, premi
 um fragrance and essential oils to personalize your candles. Whether you p
 refer floral\, fruity\, citrus or musky aromas\, we have something to matc
 h your olfactory taste.\nDecorate Your Candles: Add unique embellishments 
 to your candles such as crystals\, dried flowers\, dyes\, glitter and more
 . Paint your vessels or leave them as they are. Let your creativity shine 
 as you design your one-of-a-kind candles.\nCandle Vessel: We provide you w
 ith two 7oz glass vessels with lids and label tags\, which should get you 
 a combined burn time of approximately 50-60 hours.\nHands-On Experience: G
 et hands-on experience with each step from blending scents and sticking th
 e wicks to pouring\, and designing your candles with guidance from an expe
 rienced chandler.\nAll Materials Provided: Soy and coconut wax\, cotton wi
 cks\, fragrance oils\, decorative elements\, paint\, two glass vessels and
  all necessary supplies are included.\nSnacks & Refreshments: Enjoy from a
  selection of coffee/tea\, refreshments and snacks\, all included with you
 r ticket.\nWho Should Join: This workshop is great for beginners and candl
 e enthusiasts alike. Come on your own or with friends. No experience neede
 d.\nOur workshops are more intimate so seats are limited - Hurry to secure
  your spot today.\nGuests must be aged 12+ to participate.candle making ex
 perience at Artbox's Studio Gallery. Seats are limited\, so be sure to sec
 ure your tickets today!\nSee more events at: https://www.artboxstudiogalle
