 0-7?pid=4146\nWebsite: https://go.evvnt.com/3318590-8?pid=4146\nWebsite: h
 ttps://go.evvnt.com/3318590-9?pid=4146\nLinkedIn: https://go.evvnt.com/331
 8590-10?pid=4146\nWebsite: https://go.evvnt.com/3318590-11?pid=4146\nWebsi
 te: https://go.evvnt.com/3318590-12?pid=4146\nDate and Time: Sunday\, 12 A
 pril 2026 at 07:00 - Tuesday\, 14 April 2026 at 17:00\nVenue details: Fair
 mont Royal York\, 100 Front Street West\, Toronto\, Ontario\, M5J 1E3\, Ca
 nada\nCategory: Classes / Courses | Professional Training | Science\, Heal
 th and Medicine\nPrices:\nAVIR MEMBER FULL MEETING: USD 450.00\,\nAVIR MEM
 BER SINGLE DAY: USD 200.00\,\nAVIR MEMBER STUDENT: USD 250.00\,\nNON-MEMBE
