 7a.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Explore Kensington Market with the tour that started it all. A
 s the original food tour of one of Toronto’s quirkiest neighbourhoods\, 
 Tasty Tours takes you past the tourist traps to the family-run shops and h
 idden counters most visitors walk right past.\nOn this experience\, you’
 ll travel:\n1. Around the world\, through food – Skip the lines at a mix
  of local favourites that show off Kensington’s global roots\, from hand
 made Tibetan dumplings to flaky Jamaican patties. Thanks to our long-stand
 ing relationships with shop owners\, you’ll get priority access and cura
 ted tastings from some of the best places in the market. Come hungry – t
 his tour counts as lunch.\n2. Through stories – Trace Kensington’s jou
 rney from a Jewish market into one of Toronto’s most diverse communities
 . Each stop has a little history\, a little gossip\, and a lot of flavour.
 \n3. Through a local lens – Led by locals who know the market inside and
  out\, you’ll get insider access to hidden corners and stories that make
  the market unlike anywhere else.\nYou haven’t truly experienced Kensing
 ton Market until you’ve been on a Tasty Tour of Kensington Market. Join 
 us and discover the side of Kensington that most people miss.\n$89 per per
 son\nFree for kids under 7!
