SUMMARY:Toronto Silent Film Festival 2026
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260412T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260412T235900
UID:blogto-232323@blogto.com
DESCRIPTION:The Toronto Silent Film Festival is a volunteer-run\, not-for-
 profit founded in late 2009 by Shirley Hughes and Marc Wonnacott with the 
 vision to bring audiences and the magic of the Silent Film experience toge
 ther.\nThis year it returns to Revue Cinema from April 10 to April 12\, wi
 th many films celebrating milestone screenings! 
LOCATION:Revue Cinema
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/toronto-silent-film-festival-2026/
