  this 2.5 hour workshop\, you will learn how to cut\, shape\, and finish a
  wax piece with guidance at every step. After the class\, we can optionall
 y also cast your wax model into sterling silver\, polish and ship your fin
 ished piece directly to your home once complete.\nPricing: Please note tha
 t casting your final wax piece is optional\, and will include additional c
 asting costs based on the gram weight of the final piece.\nWhile we would 
 love to offer casting options in non-precious materials\, our casting part
 ners currently only offer casting in sterling silver\, and 14k and 18k gol
 d. Typical sterling silver casting costs ranges from $55 to $125\, dependi
 ng on the weight of your design. We’re happy to recommend lighter\, more
  delicate options if preferred\, however\, choosing to cast your piece is 
