BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Board Game Designer Night at Wychwood Pub in Midtown Toronto
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260415T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260415T220000
UID:blogto-232912@blogto.com
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://blogto-production2-baselayer-display.blo
 gto.com/events/2026/03/30/original_imagedbfba4d7-5a90-4937-a3a4-b8fdb010d3
 db.jpg
DESCRIPTION:We invite you to join us for a fun night of testing out intere
 sting new board games in the process of being designed. Bring your own des
 ign and we'll do our best to ensure everyone gets their turn on the table!
 \nWhether you're a seasoned gamer or new to the world of board games\, eve
 ryone has useful feedback to provide. Test out new games\, challenge your 
 friends\, and make new connections with fellow board game lovers along the
  way. Come as a group or solo and we can help pair you with a community ta
 ble. Our events are a great way to connect with members of local communiti
 es and are perfect for folks arriving in Toronto looking to meet new peopl
 e.\nThanks to the generosity of Wychwood Pub\, we will be enjoying the use
  of their space for our night of learning and playtesting new\, in-process
  board games. Wychwood Pub has a menu with food and both alcoholic and non
 alcoholic beverages that you can order from while we’re having fun playi
 ng games. This event is Pay-What-You-Can (minimum $5)\, with more details 
 available at the link to the Changeling Gaming Events Eventbrite (see webs
 ite link).\nTo learn more\, find Changeling Gaming Events Toronto on Event
 brite or click the website link to see this event (see right side on deskt
 op/above on mobile).
LOCATION:Wychwood Pub
