SUMMARY:The Night Circus Presents: LE CABARET BLEU-Le Jardin des Papillons
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260416T200000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260416T233000
UID:blogto-232841@blogto.com
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://blogto-production2-baselayer-display.blo
 gto.com/events/2026/03/29/original_image25ded3a4-3d44-41bc-814b-3d93efd9d1
 fa.jpg
DESCRIPTION:A VINTAGE CABARET SOIREE! Featuring our live jazz band and Tor
 onto's finest cabaret talent.\n🎪 The Night Circus Toronto Presents: Le 
 Cabaret Bleu – Le Jardin des Papillons\n📅 April 16th\n📍 The Painte
 d Lady\, Toronto\n⏰ 8:00 PM – Late\n✨ Pre-show: 8:30 PM | Show Start
 : 9 PM\n🎟 Seating first come\, first serve!\nTickets\nAdvance Tickets: 
 $25 (LIMITED)\nTier 1 Tickets: $30 (LIMITED)\nTier 2 Tickets: $35 (LIMITED
 )\nThis spring\, step into something softer\, sweeter\, and just a little 
 bit surreal.\nWhether you're welcoming the season in bloom or looking for 
 a night of beauty and escape\, Le Cabaret Bleu: Le Jardin des Papillons is
  your invitation into a dreamlike garden after dark. Consider this your wh
 imsical prelude to spring — or your main event.\nStep through the velvet
  curtain into un jardin enchanté\, where fluttering butterflies\, bloomin
 g florals\, and cabaret magic intertwine. Think pastel decadence\, shimmer
 ing wings\, delicate petals\, and just enough mischief to keep things inte
 resting.\n🎶 La Musique\nOur live jazz ensemble will fill the room with 
 airy swing\, romantic melodies\, and rhythms that feel like a warm spring 
 breeze. Expect lush brass\, dreamy vocals\, and a soundtrack made for danc
 ing among the blossoms.\n💃 Les Performeurs\nDazzling burlesque and caba
 ret artists will drift through the evening like butterflies in bloom — s
 parkling\, sensual\, and impossible to look away from. Petals fall\, wings
  shimmer\, and the line between stage and audience disappears.\n🍸 Les S
 howgirl Shots\nOur glamorous showgirls will flutter through the room with 
 playful shots in hand\, inviting you to sip\, toast\, and indulge in true 
 cabaret fashion. A little sweetness\, a little sparkle\, and a touch of sp
 ring magic.\n🎭 Plus qu’un spectacle\nInteractive games\, загадк
 и\, and playful surprises await throughout the venue. Collect raffle tick
 ets for your chance to win enchanting prizes — because every garden hold
 s a few secrets.\n🦋 Tenue de Jardin\nFlorals\, pastels\, soft silks\, s
 parkling wings\, garden glamour — dress like you’ve just emerged from 
 a butterfly dream. The more whimsical\, the better.\n🗓 April 16th\n📍
  The Painted Lady\n⏰ Same time\, same place\nWelcome the season in style
 .\nLet the petals fall\, the wings flutter\, and the magic bloom.\nLe Caba
 ret Bleu vous attend. 🦋✨
LOCATION:The Painted Lady
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/the-night-circus-presents-le-cabaret-ble
 u-le-jardin-des-papillons-toronto/
X-SOURCE:blogTO
