BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Blood On the Clocktower at The Grand Order of Divine Sweets in Wes
 t End TO
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260417T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260417T220000
UID:blogto-232899@blogto.com
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://blogto-production2-baselayer-display.blo
 gto.com/events/2026/03/30/original_imagee510215c-9f16-44a5-9b65-fbde44bd03
 05.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Whether you're a seasoned gamer or new to the world of social 
 deception games\, this event offers something for everyone. Come solo or w
 ith friends and immerse yourself in a game of Blood on the Clocktower. Our
  events are a great way to connect with members of local communities and a
 re perfect for folks arriving in Toronto looking to make new connections.\
 nWhat is Blood on the Clocktower? - Blood on the Clocktower is an advanced
  version of the game Werewolf\, where crucially\, the dead still have an i
 mportant role to play in the game. The game is run by a Storyteller who ha
 s carefully crafted an experience and facilitates the game for up to 20 pl
 ayers. It is part deduction and part deception. Set in the town of Ravensw
 ood Bluff\, players in the game assume different roles\, each with unique 
 abilities to hunt down evil or manipulate the townsfolk.\nThanks to the ge
 nerosity of the Grand Order of Divine Sweets\, we will be taking over the 
 front of their chocolate shop for a deliciously fun night of Blood on the 
 Clocktower! Included in the price of admission is one free beverage and at
  least one game of Blood on the Clocktower\, though we’ll play as much a
 s we can! Tickets are $20 for the night or $13.50 for Changeling Special E
 vents Members.\nIf you have not played before or are newer to the game\, t
 here will be a quick tutorial at the top of the event to learn how to play
  and ask any questions from the Storyteller.\nWe will be playing our custo
 m beginner-friendly script Changeling's Introduction at this event.\nAge r
 ecommendation\, 16 years +\nTo learn more\, find Changeling Gaming Events 
 Toronto on Eventbrite or click the website link to see this event (see rig
 ht side on desktop/above on mobile).
LOCATION:The Grand Order of Divine Sweets
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/blood-on-the-clocktower-at-the-grand-ord
 er-of-divine-sweets-in-west-end-to-toronto-13/
X-SOURCE:blogTO
END:VEVENT
