 wery\, we will have plenty of space for the night to play board games! Tic
 kets for this event are $10.00 or free for Changeling Members\, and includ
 e access to the gameplay area\, a curated collection of board games\, and 
 on-site game experts who can help you with player introductions\, game sel
 ection\, and running how-to-plays for your table.\nTo learn more\, find Ch
 angeling Gaming Events Toronto on Eventbrite or click the website link to 
 see this event (see right side on desktop/above on mobile).
