BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Chaotic Good.
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260417T230000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260417T235900
UID:blogto-233472@blogto.com
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://blogto-production2-baselayer-display.blo
 gto.com/events/2026/04/11/original_imageedc8788a-6896-48c2-8217-ef50c70a65
 95.jpg
DESCRIPTION:GOOD COMEDY!\nWe survived the longest winter and 2 Mercury ret
 rogrades that humbled us. Spring is finally clocking in (barely) but your 
 Hinge roster is dry and your group chat is tired of you. Come spiral in a 
 place that supports your chaos! Chaotic Good is back this month with anoth
 er STACKED lineup of 8 headliners doing their best 7 minutes on a show so 
 good\, it’s chaotic!\nFEATURING\nRebecca Reeds (Roast Battle Canada\, Th
 e Villain was Right)\nAllie Pearse (Halifax Comedy Festival\, Just For Lau
 ghs)\nJuliana Rodrigues (Just For Laughs\, SiriusXM)\nRyan Dillon (Just Fo
 r Laughs\, Kevin Hart’s Laugh Out Loud)\nKyle Patan (Grindstone Comedy F
 estival\, Just For Laughs Vancouver)\nAmy Bugg (Winnipeg Comedy Festival\,
  San Francisco Sketchfest)\nLiam Andres (Just For Laughs Toronto\, Yuk Yuk
