BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:How Meditation Can Transform Your Life Free Talk With Guided Medit
 ation
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260417T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260417T210000
UID:blogto-231895@blogto.com
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://blogto-production2-baselayer-display.blo
 gto.com/events/2026/03/08/original_image7ed0640f-7d02-46e3-ab1b-928fe93626
 91.jpg
DESCRIPTION:✨ Discover the “Portable Paradise Within” - An Evening o
 f Meditation & Inner Peace | SRF Toronto\n⸻\nOverview\n⸻\nDid you know
  that deep inner peace\, joy\, and clarity are not things you need to chas
 e\, but experiences you can learn to access within yourself?\nJoin us for 
 a special evening with Self-Realization Fellowship monk Brother Jayananda 
 as he shares timeless meditation teachings that have inspired seekers arou
 nd the world. Through wisdom\, practical insights\, and a guided meditatio
 n\, you will explore how meditation can awaken a deep calmness and spiritu
 al awareness that transforms everyday life.\nParamahansa Yogananda- author
  of the spiritual classic Autobiography of a Yogi - described meditation a
 s a way to carry a “portable paradise within.” Imagine being able to e
 xperience peace and joy wherever you are\, regardless of circumstances.\nW
 hether you are completely new to meditation or have practiced for years\, 
 this event offers a rare opportunity to experience these teachings directl
 y.\n⸻\nWhat to Expect\n⸻\n✨ Inspiring talk by a senior Self-Realizat
 ion Fellowship monk with over 45 years of spiritual experience\n🧘 Guide
 d meditation suitable for beginners and experienced meditators\n🌿 Pract
 ical insights on how meditation can bring calm\, clarity\, and balance to 
 daily life\n📖 Introduction to the Kriya Yoga meditation teachings of Pa
 ramahansa Yogananda\n💫 A welcoming environment for anyone curious about
  meditation and spiritual growth\n⸻\nAbout the Teachings\n⸻\nParamahan
 sa Yogananda founded Self-Realization Fellowship (SRF) in 1920 to share th
 e universal science of Kriya Yoga meditation. His teachings emphasize the 
 direct experience of the Divine within and the underlying unity of all rel
 igions and all life.\n⸻\nYour Speaker\n⸻\nBrother Jayananda\, whose na
 me means “attainment of bliss through being victorious”\, has been a m
 onk in the Self-Realization Fellowship monastic order for over 45 years.\n
 He currently serves as minister-in-charge of the SRF Hollywood Temple and 
 has traveled widely across North America and Europe\, offering lectures\, 
 retreats\, and inspirational programs on the teachings of Paramahansa Yoga
 nanda.\nEvent Details\n📍 Latvian Canadian Centre\n4 Credit Union Drive\
 nNorth York\, ON M4A 2N8\n🚗 Free parking available at the venue\n🎟 A
 dmission: Free
LOCATION:Latvian Canadian Centre
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/how-meditation-can-transform-your-life-f
 ree-talk-with-guided-meditation-toronto/
X-SOURCE:blogTO
END:VEVENT
