 d2.jpg
DESCRIPTION:The Assembly is an interactive theatre-meets-board-game experi
 ence about sustainability and democracy designed for youth ages 10 and up\
 , where theatre\, strategy\, and social activism meet!\nNominated for five
  Dora Mavor Moore awards in 2025\, Crossroads Theatre is bringing The Asse
 mbly back to Weston this Spring!\n📆 Friday\, April 17th ⏰ 4:30PM\n
 📆 Saturday\, May 2nd - 2 performances! ⏰ 11AM & 2PM\n🎟️ Pay What
  You Can!\nAbout the show:\nDuring every performance\, audience members fo
 rm The Assembly\, where they are invited to work together to balance their
  city’s current needs with the needs of future generations. This show is
  a fun\, cooperative 60-minute challenge that gives audience members the c
 hance to collaborate\, deepen their empathy\, and understand their impact 
 on future generations.
