  FOR YOUR APPROVAL!\nIT'S LIKE A REGULAR XXX EDITION OF LATE NIGHT FUCKERY
  BUT A CUMPETITION AND IT'S IN THE WEST END!\nCUM SEE US!\nAn adults only 
 late night comedy show where the comics let it all out.\nWe've got Toronto
