 5e.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Canada’s premier Latin music and dance club invites you to e
 xperience an unforgettable night of salsa — dinner\, dancing\, and live 
 music all under one roof!\nBook a table for dinner and dancing\, or arrive
  after 9 PM to head straight to the dance floor.\nEvening Schedule\n� 7:
 00 PM – Doors open for dinner and drinks\n� 9:00 PM – Salsa lesson w
 ith Teria Morada (no partner needed!)\n� 10:00 PM – First live salsa s
 et\, with a second set at midnight\n� 11:00 PM – Keep the energy going
  with DJ Van Gogh spinning Top 40\, salsa\, and Latin hits\nAbout the Band
 \nLed by founding member Cali-born bassist Fhanor Molina\, Latin Swing Orc
 hestra is one of Toronto’s favourite classic salsa ensembles and a torch
 bearer of modern salsa and topical music\, igniting the legacy of these ge
 nres with a contemporary twist.\nWhy Lula is unique:\nThe only venue of it
 s kind in North America\, Lula Lounge features a rotating roster of more t
 han a dozen full salsa orchestras every Friday and Saturday—year-round. 
 Our stage welcomes the best local talent alongside special guests from acr
 oss Canada and the Americas\, offering a one-of-a-kind salsa experience in
