BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Somewhere Along The Way Film and Concert
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260418T103000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260418T124500
UID:blogto-232202@blogto.com
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://blogto-production2-baselayer-display.blo
 gto.com/events/2026/03/15/original_image9708ada2-b060-46dc-a91d-6d92078968
 41.jpg
DESCRIPTION:A SPECIAL CAMINO DE SANTIAGO EVENT – FILM AND LIVE CONCERT\n
 A powerful new documentary\, Somewhere Along The Way\, invites audiences t
 o walk the legendary Camino de Santiago — one of the world’s most famo
 us pilgrimages — through the eyes\, reflections\, and heart of Australia
 n musician and broadcaster Dan Mullins.\nFilmed across the breathtaking la
 ndscapes of Northern Spain\, Somewhere Along The Way is more than a travel
  film. It’s an emotional exploration of why thousands of people from aro
 und the world walk the Camino each year — seeking purpose\, peace\, and 
 personal transformation.\nGuided by Mullins’ deeply personal narration\,
  the film captures the physical beauty of the trail\, the timeless culture
  of the villages along the way\, and the moving stories of the people who 
 walk it. Every pilgrim has their own reason for taking the first step — 
 grief\, faith\, curiosity\, or renewal — and this documentary captures t
 he shared humanity that binds them somewhere along the way.\nSomewhere Alo
 ng The Way invites audiences to experience the Camino for themselves — t
 hrough the stories\, landscapes\, and moments that define it. Whether you
 ’ve walked the trail\, dream of doing so\, or simply love stories that e
 xplore courage\, connection\, and transformation\, this film captures the 
 true spirit of what it means to journey with purpose.\nAbout Dan Mullins\n
 Dan Mullins is an Australian singer-songwriter\, broadcaster\, and author 
 whose music and storytelling have inspired pilgrims worldwide. His hit son
 g “Somewhere Along The Way” became an anthem for Camino walkers\, cele
 brating the emotional journey of rediscovery that defines the trail.\nJoin
  us to watch the film\, and hear Dan Mullins play live. It's an entertaini
 ng way to find out more about the Camino!
LOCATION:Fox Theatre
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/somewhere-along-the-way-film-and-concert
 -toronto-2/
X-SOURCE:blogTO
END:VEVENT
