BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:A Resin on Canvas Workshop
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260419T173000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260419T193000
UID:blogto-232597@blogto.com
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://blogto-production2-baselayer-display.blo
 gto.com/events/2026/03/23/original_image3303fccc-0d9a-4848-9148-580f97889b
 09.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Mix and pour your art at this vibrant resin art experience\, w
 here you’ll create a stunning resin masterpiece on canvas with your own 
 personal flair.\nWhat to Expect:\nExplore the beauty of resin as you desig
 n your canvas using a wide variety of dyes\, pigments\, crystals\, gold/si
 lver leaf\, glitters\, metallic flakes\, and other embellishments.\nThe fi
 rst hour will be dedicated to planning and designing your composition. You
 ’ll then mix\, pour\, and layer your resin to bring your artwork to life
  with beautiful\, fluid effects.\nCreative Techniques:\nLearn how to prope
 rly measure\, mix\, tint\, and pour resin onto canvas. Our instructor will
  guide you through layering techniques\, movement methods\, and how to ach
 ieve depth\, shimmer\, and dimension.\nAll materials are included:\nProfes
 sional-grade resin\nCanvas\nPigments and decorative elements\, including g
 old/silver leaf and glass crystals\nGloves\, a respirator mask and protect
 ive equipment\nTools and supplies needed for your project\nParticipants ar
 e welcome to bring small\, lightweight mementos (such as photos or sentime
 ntal items) to incorporate into their art.\nSnacks & Refreshments: Complim
 entary tea\, coffee\, water\, and light snacks will be available.\nWho Sho
 uld Join: Open to ages 12+. No experience necessary.\n(Participants under 
 16 must be accompanied by at least one paying adult.)\nCuring & Pickup:\nY
 our canvas is best to remain at the studio to cure properly. Pieces will b
 e ready for pickup the following weekend to allow for full curing and fini
 shing. If pickup isn't possible\, participants can receive a to go box at 
 their own risk or shipping is available for an additional fee based on loc
 ation.\nResin Workshop Disclaimer:\nResin is a sensitive medium that requi
 res careful attention to detail. It is very important to listen closely an
 d follow all instructions to ensure the success of your artwork. Improper 
 mixing or missed steps may result in pieces that do not cure properly.\nIf
  adjustments are needed\, our team can assist with repairs for a small fee
 \, or you may attend another workshop at a discounted rate to recreate you
 r piece or add an additional resin layer after your artwork has cured.\nSp
 aces are limited — reserve your spot today.\nSee more events at: https:/
 /www.artboxstudiogallery.com/calendar\nCall us at: 647-617-9550
LOCATION:Artbox Studio Gallery
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/a-resin-on-canvas-workshop-toronto/
X-SOURCE:blogTO
