 ram.\nFrom North India vs South India to Delhi vs Mumbai and India vs Paki
 stan — no region is safe\, no stereotype is sacred\, and no one is calli
 ng a truce.\nThis isn’t just a roast show.\nIt’s every family WhatsApp
  argument.\nIt’s every wedding side-eye.\nIt’s every “beta\, in our 
 days…” speech — weaponized.\nFirst Gen Desis vs F.O.Bs.\nPunjabi vol
 ume vs Gujarati math.\nComedians seen on JFL\, SiriusXM\, Netflix\, Prime 
 & Crave go head-to-head with savage burns\, brutal comebacks\, and hilario
 usly unfiltered desi banter.\nIf you’ve ever fought about whose state ha
 s better food\, whose parents sacrificed more\, or whether Mumbai or Delhi
  has more “vibe” — this show is for you.\nFor one night\, Comedy Bar
  Bloor turns into your living room during cricket season.\nLimited seats. 
 Unlimited trauma.\nPlease note: Content in Hindi\, Hinglish & English.\n$2
 0 online\, $25 at the door.
