 co dancers\, Toronto’s Makeda Benitez and Vancouver’s Kirill Deljanin\
 , presenting new choreographic works. Accompanying the dance are celebrate
 d Toronto singer Shirlita “La Pili\,” legendary Toronto guitarist Nico
 las Hernández\, and Seville-based percussionist Dani Carbonell. F for Fam
 ilia is the joyful finale of the festival – a celebration of community a
 nd the art that binds us together.\nARTISTS:\n​Makeda Benitez - Dance\nK
