 f3.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Step out of the daily rush and reconnect with what truly nouri
 shes you—mind\, body\, and soul. Foundations of You is an intimate\, 3-h
 our wellness experience designed to help you pause\, reflect\, and reset. 
 Through guided journaling\, holistic coaching\, embodiment practices\, and
  personal reflection\, you’ll explore your current habits\, identify are
 as of imbalance\, and create sustainable steps to support your wellbeing.\
 nEnjoy a curated wellness bar\, a guided visualization\, integration exerc
 ises\, and a thoughtfully prepared take-home goodie bag valued at $100+. W
 ith space to connect\, reflect\, and gain clarity\, you’ll leave feeling
  grounded\, supported\, and empowered to prioritize yourself in a meaningf
 ul way.\nThis experience is perfect for anyone feeling overwhelmed\, disco
 nnected\, or ready to invest in their wellbeing with intention.
