 gto.com/events/2026/03/17/original_imagecbb7689e-89a3-498f-ad9f-f535d338cc
 22.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Greek Wine Week returns to Toronto from April 19 to 25\, bring
 ing a citywide lineup of tastings\, dinners\, and events focused on modern
  Greek wine.\nThe week features over 20 events across the city\, including
  walk-around tastings\, curated wine pairing dinners\, and late-night part
 ies. Eight wineries will be travelling from Greece to host tastings\, meet
  guests\, and share their wines directly.\nExpect a strong focus on indige
 nous varietals like Assyrtiko\, Xinomavro\, Agiorgitiko\, and Malagouzia\,
  presented through both casual and more in-depth experiences. Events range
  from large social gatherings like the Parea Party to more intimate\, chef
 -driven dinners and industry masterclasses.\nFor anyone curious about Gree
 k wine or looking to discover something new\, the festival offers a rare c
 hance to explore a category that remains underrepresented but increasingly
  relevant on Toronto wine lists.\nA full schedule of events is available a
 t greekwineweek.com.
LOCATION:Multiple Venues
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/greek-wine-week-toronto-3/
X-SOURCE:blogTO
END:VEVENT
