BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Sicilian Festa by Erica Foffi
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260419T183000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260419T230000
UID:blogto-229054@blogto.com
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://blogto-production2-baselayer-display.blo
 gto.com/events/2026/01/09/original_imaged1195048-a70c-435b-8487-fa01a19294
 eb.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate the colours and flavours of Sicily with three dishes
  that capture the island’s rich culinary heritage. This is food full of 
 sunshine and tradition — recipes that have travelled through generations
  and still bring people together around the table.\nIn this hands-on class
 \, you’ll prepare:\nCaponata\nThe classic Sicilian sweet-and-sour eggpla
 nt dish with celery\, capers\, and vinegar\, a perfect balance of bold fla
 vours.\nArancini\nGolden fried rice balls with ragù\, mozzarella\, and se
 asonal fillings — the street food royalty of Sicily. (Vegetarian variati
 on available)\nCannoli\nCrisp pastry shells filled with sweet ricotta crea
 m and decorated with candied fruit or chocolate. Learn how to make an amaz
 ing ricotta cream and decorate your cannoli.\nParticipants will work in pa
 irs and small groups\, and leave with recipes\, confidence\, and a little 
 piece of Sicily in their hearts.\n-----\nErica Foffi was born and raised i
 n Rome\, where cooking was part of daily life\, a way to connect\, celebra
 te\, and show love. After moving to Toronto\, she began inviting friends i
 nto her kitchen to share the traditional dishes she grew up with. What sta
 rted around her table soon became a way to teach others about the richness
  of Italian home cooking and the joy of gathering together around good foo
 d.\nHer classes are hands-on\, welcoming\, and rooted in tradition. Erica 
 focuses on simple\, honest food made with care\, from street food classics
  to handmade pastas\, and on creating a relaxed space where anyone can fee
 l confident and inspired in the kitchen.\n@cookingwitherica_  |  ericaital
 iancookin.wixsite.com\n-----\nEvery week\, The Depanneur invites TO’s be
 st culinary talents to lead fun\, hands-on workshops. @thedepanneur
LOCATION:The Depanneur
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/sicilian-festa-by-erica-foffi-toronto-2/
X-SOURCE:blogTO
END:VEVENT
