 oronto Arab Orchestra presents Diwan: An Ode to Sufism\, a special concert
  that pays tribute to Sufism in Arabic and Persian poetry. Directed by Gab
 y Al Botros\, the concert features vocalist Habib Hoseini and the singers 
 of the Toronto Arab Orchestra choir. The orchestra will be joined by the T
 oronto Daf Ensemble\, led by Zohreh Shahbazy.\nDiwan is an original orches
