BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Prince - Exactly 10 Years Later - A Toronto Tribute
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260421T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260421T235500
UID:blogto-232722@blogto.com
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://blogto-production2-baselayer-display.blo
 gto.com/events/2026/03/26/original_image629bbc5b-9ede-4c34-9202-c1e3fe0181
 d2.jpg
DESCRIPTION:On this day 10 years ago - April 21\, 2016 - we lost Prince.\n
 Prince Rogers Nelson — the Purple One\, the Genius of Paisley Park\, the
  man who could make a guitar weep and a crowd lose their minds with a sing
 le glance — left this world exactly 10 years ago on this day.\nOn the 10
 th anniversary of his heartbreaking departure\, we gather not to mourn\, b
 ut to celebrate the immortal fire he lit in all of us.\nCome honor his unp
 aralleled life.\nCome rejoice in his revolutionary career.\nCome feel the 
 thunder of his impact — the way he shattered boundaries\, rewrote the ru
 les of music\, fashion\, sexuality\, and freedom itself.\nCome stand in aw
 e of the unstoppable legacy that still echoes through every stage\, every 
 playlist\, and every bold soul brave enough to be unapologetically themsel
 ves. This is Prince.\nThis is forever. Let’s make the 10th anniversary a
  celebration worthy of the legend.\n#Prince10Forever\nWe'll celebrate ever
 ything Prince in Toronto's Corso Italia neighbourhood.\n****FREE!***\nAll 
 Prince\, all night 7pm to near midnight. Come celebrate with other fans. S
 t. Clair West just off Dufferin.\nBIG Audio - an amazing presentation\nBIG
  Video - on 8 HUGE screens\nHOURLY Prince door prizes - unique gifts you w
 ill love\nFUN drink specials\nAll Prince's biggest hits for 4+ straight ho
 urs\, with a room full of other fans. A multi-screen video presentation wi
 th most video hits in original formats\, with side screens with unique Pri
 nce footage.\n****FREE!***\nPlease note - this is a tribute night featurin
 g licensed audio and video. No live band or artist appearance or performan
 ce is planned or anticipated.
LOCATION:The Cat's Cradle
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/prince-exactly-10-years-later-a-toronto-
 tribute-toronto/
X-SOURCE:blogTO
END:VEVENT
