DESCRIPTION:Get ready TORONTO🔥\nMOTION TOUR w/SPINALL is coming to your
  city!\nAfrobeats heavyweight SPINALL is bringing the Lagos party energy a
 cross Canada this April. Expect nothing but premium vibes\, big sounds\, a
 nd unforgettable nights.\nSPINALL is one of Africa’s most recognizable a
 nd successful DJs. The DJ\, producer and songwriter\, with his signature A
 frican cap\, is well known for his large catalogue of hit singles\, his su
 preme skills on the decks and for collaborations across six studio albums.
 \nHe is one of the few African DJs to tour Africa\, UK & The United States
  including performances at Ends\, One Africa\, two weekends at Coachella a
 nd Glastonbury Festivals. SPINALL who opened for Bruno mars in Australia h
 as just headlined the 2022 MTV EMA’s in Germany performing his hit recor
 d Power featuring Summer Walker\, DJ Snake\, Ayanna and Nasty C. SPINALL
 ’s signature style moniker\, a traditional Yoruba cap\, fostered the AKA
  “The CAP” which also doubles as an acronym for “The Crazy Ass Party
 ”\, a common reference used by fans after their experiences at SPINALL
 ’s events.\nFor more events and details\, Visit: www.afrobass.com/events
