 1f.jpg
DESCRIPTION:To mark the opening of Colourful Parachutes: Imagining Alterna
 tive Futures Through the Power of Play\, join curator Frances Loeffler\, C
 urator of Exhibitions at The Power Plant Contemporary Art Gallery\, for a 
 conversation with participating artists.\nTogether\, they will reflect on 
 the ideas behind their works and the exhibition’s exploration of play as
  a radical and transformative force. Imagining children as the primary aud
 ience\, Colourful Parachutes asks how the conventions of the gallery might
  shift when curiosity\, experimentation\, and imagination take the lead.
LOCATION:The Power Plant
