 relax\, have fun\, and create meaningful artwork side by side—whether yo
 u’re painting connecting canvases or each others portraits. Each experie
 nce offers its own creative twist\; be sure to check the event link for fu
 ll details.\nFollow along with a trained artist while each partner creates
  their own artwork designed to connect or complement one another. Guests a
 re encouraged to add their own colours and personal touches\, making each 
 piece truly unique. All supplies are included\, including aprons\, brushes
 \, paints\, and materials\, and complimentary water is provided. The exper
 ience takes place in a cozy\, inspiring studio atmosphere designed for a r
 elaxed and enjoyable night out.\nThis experience is perfect for couples lo
 oking for a fun\, outside-the-box date night. No prior painting experience
  is needed. Participants must be 18+ to attend.\nSpaces are limited—rese
 rve your spots and create something meaningful together.\nSee more events 
 at: https://www.artboxstudiogallery.com/calendar\nCall us at: 647-617-9550
