 g with DJ Van Gogh spinning Top 40\, salsa\, and Latin hits\nAbout the Ban
 d\nLa Borinqueña Orquestra’s big salsa sound is inspired by the classic
  repertoire of Puerto Rico. Hard-hitting tunes and intense rhythmic drive 
 cater to the dancers in the crowd. Catchy melodies and impactful horn arra
 ngements come together in a perfect blend of vintage and bold salsa styles
 \nWhy Lula is unique:\nThe only venue of its kind in North America\, Lula 
 Lounge features a rotating roster of more than a dozen full salsa orchestr
 as every Friday and Saturday—year-round. Our stage welcomes the best loc
 al talent alongside special guests from across Canada and the Americas\, o
 ffering a one-of-a-kind salsa experience in a warm\, colourful\, and inclu
 sive space.
LOCATION:Lula Lounge
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/salsa-saturday-w-la-borinquena-dj-van-go
 gh-dance-to-live-toronto-4/
