BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tiny's Session
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260426T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260426T220000
UID:blogto-233427@blogto.com
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://blogto-production2-baselayer-display.blo
 gto.com/events/2026/04/10/original_image6984b136-38b3-4a7b-8df4-4bc0bcb7b4
 4c.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Toronto's most intimate live music and comedy series. A curate
 d lineup of emerging artists performing for a room full of people who came
  to feel something.\nTiny's Session started in 2023 as a condo living room
  vibe sesh. Since then\, we've turned rooftops\, barbershops\, patios\, bo
 utiques and cafes into stages for soulful music\, spoken word\, and stand-
 up comedy.\nInspired by formats like NPR's Tiny Desk Concerts\, we bring t
 he living room energy everywhere we go\; a cozy\, personal setting where t
 he artist is close enough to make eye contact and the audience is part of 
 the show.\nWHAT TO EXPECT\n3 MUSIC ACTS\, 1 COMEDIAN Every artist on the s
 tage was handpicked. Multiple genres\, multiple vibes — one thing in com
 mon: they're worth your full attention.\nDOORS AT 6:00 PM · SHOW AT 6:30 
