BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Toronto Dating Hub April Speed Dating for Professionals: Ages 30-4
 5
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260427T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260427T220000
UID:blogto-233406@blogto.com
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://blogto-production2-baselayer-display.blo
 gto.com/events/2026/04/09/original_image56ca7d1c-be7a-42de-bfdf-2571e2ad32
 c4.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Get up to 20 mini dates with likeminded singles (aged 30-45) w
 ho fit our criteria in a chic bar in King W. Perfect for introverted peopl
 e.\nJoin one of Toronto Dating Hub's best sellers - try our April speed da
 ting event to get up to 20 mini dates with likeminded GTA singles (aged 30
 -45) at a chic King West restaurant & bar - Oria on King.\nThis event will
  feature both speed dating & open mingling so attendees form meaningful co
 nnections!\nCome mix & mingle with like-minded GTA professional singles.\n
 *To curate a high quality group of professional singles\, you must have at
  least FOUR of the following criteria (you will indicate this in the order
  form):\nSerious about dating / ready and looking for a long term relation
 ship\nGraduated from a university or college with at least 1 degree/diplom
 a\nLives on your own (whether you rent or own)\n5 or more years of experti
 se in your specific career/field\nAnnual income/earnings of $75K or more\n
 Truly passionate about your career (not "stuck working in a 9-5 you hate")
 \nStarted your own business(es) at least 1 year ago\nHas had meaningful re
 lationships before (not socially awkward) - if you're not sure about this 
 - book a consult/email!!\nWhat to expect at our event:\nA dedicated and ex
 perienced event host & emcee - Andrea Lo\nIcebreakers and intros\nSpeed da
 ting rounds (only 1-1.5 hr to keep it light)\nOpen mingling so you talk to
  anyone you missed or spend more time with someone\nDigital match form\nAl
 l will be explained at the event. Please attend the full 3 hours to not im
 pact the speed dating rounds.\nOnly 40 spots in total to keep it intimate!
 \nOur tickets tend to sell out quickly so to allow others the opportunity 
 to join AND to curate more variety for each event\, attendees are only all
 owed to attend UP TO 3 of our singles events PER MONTH (only 1 speed datin
 g event within that). Please email torontodatinghub@gmail.com to get appro
 val to attend more than 3 events before purchasing more tickets. Thanks fo
 r allowing others to experience our events and to meet that special someon
 e!\n✨ *Please note: These criteria are intended as a guideline to help u
 s curate a fun\, respectful\, and high-quality group of singles. We do not
  fact-check or verify the personal information provided by attendees\, but
  we trust guests to be honest and come with the right intentions. The even
 t experience depends on everyone’s participation\, and while we aim to g
 ather like-minded singles\, we cannot guarantee specific outcomes\, matche
 s\, or personal compatibility. What we can promise is a great vibe\, a cha
 nce to meet interesting & likeminded people\, and the possibility of spark
 s flying!\nFeeling nervous cause you've never been to a singles event? Not
  sure what to say/ how to get noticed?\nSign up for a 30 min coaching sess
 ion for a special promo price of $30 + HST (saving >45% off) to help prepa
 re you for the event and to better your chances to geting (more) matches. 
 Email us at torontodatinghub@gmail.com to book this or add this option to 
 your cart when you check out!\nOr add the "Mini Attendee Profile" option t
 o your cart. Want to know who's attending and get the 411 on them so you c
 an figure out who you want to spend more time with? i.e. age\, job title\,
  criteria - info that attendees opted in to share.\nhttps://www.torontoeve
 nthub.com/events
LOCATION:Oria on King
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/toronto-dating-hub-april-speed-dating-fo
 r-professionals-ages-30-45-toronto/
