 51.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Exempt from international climate agreements and rarely scruti
 nized in mainstream reporting\, the Pentagon is the world’s single large
 st institutional polluter—spewing carbon\, contaminating water\, and sca
 rring landscapes across the globe. Combining investigative journalism\, st
 riking visuals\, and stories from impacted communities\, this film challen
 ges audiences to rethink the hidden costs of a global military empire and 
 its planetary consequences. Provocative\, urgent\, and eye-opening\, this 
 is a documentary that will change how you see both the military and enviro
 nmentalism. Pay what you can ticket: https://luma.com/2utm0gdn
LOCATION:Innis Cafe
