 20.jpg
DESCRIPTION:On Wednesday\, April 29\, at 6pm\, Auberge du Pommier hosts a 
 vibrant evening celebrating one of Canada’s most influential wine produc
 ers: Pearl Morissette. Renowned for its uncompromising philosophy and site
 ‑driven approach\, the Niagara estate has become a benchmark for modern 
 Canadian winemaking\, continually reshaping how we understand terroir in t
 his country.\nGuests will be guided through six wines that showcase the re
 markable breadth and personality of the Pearl Morissette portfolio\, from 
 textured\, mineral‑driven whites to soulful\, energetic reds. Ludovic Ga
 rnier\, sommelier and longtime advocate for the estate\, will lead the eve
 ning’s tasting and share insight into the winery’s distinctive vision 
 and practices. To complement the wines\, Chef Kane Van Ee has crafted a fi
 ve‑course tasting menu\, designed to highlight the vitality\, purity\, a
 nd nuance of each pairing.\nEach ticket includes:\nFive-course tasting men
 u\nSix wine pairings from Pearl Morissette\nGuided tasting notes for each 
 pairing\nComplimentary parking\nTickets are $300 per person (including tax
  and gratuity).\nCome share in an evening shaped by thoughtful cooking\, e
 xpressive wines\, and the stories behind them. Secure your seat: https://w
 ww.aubergedupommier.com/news/wine-dinner-pearl-morissette/
LOCATION:Auberge du Pommier
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/auberge-du-pommier-x-pearl-morissette-wi
 ne-dinner-toronto/
