 t inspires you\, alongside like-minded folks.\n​​​Open Studio is mor
 e than a creative outlet. It’s a place to find rest\, connection\, and a
  little relief from daily pressures—a communal experience rooted in care
  and play.\n​​​A portion of proceeds from each will be donated to th
 e Parkdale Food Bank\, supporting nourishment and community care in our ne
 ighbourhood.\n​​​Let’s create together.\n​​​About Re-Work\n
