BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:NBS Gala 2026: Kaleidoscope
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260430T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260430T230000
UID:blogto-232934@blogto.com
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://blogto-production2-baselayer-display.blo
 gto.com/events/2026/03/31/original_image57ae743c-9324-4cc8-8962-b7b604509e
 ac.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Join us for NBS Gala 2026: Kaleidoscope\, a not-to-be-missed e
 vent in support of Canada's National Ballet School (NBS).\n\nThe Gala will
  be a memorable evening celebrating the vibrant future of ballet. Like a k
 aleidoscope\, ballet is in constant motion. With every turn\, perspectives
  shift\, colours reconfigure\, and new possibilities emerge.\n\nParty tick
 ets include a unique performance featuring Professional Ballet Program stu
 dents of all ages\, followed by a live DJ dance party. Additionally\, gues
 ts will enjoy an all-night host bar\, cocktail hour canapés and late nigh
 t gourmet bites.\n\nWe offer a range of ticket options starting at $150 an
 d Box and Mezz Seat tickets are eligible for a partial tax receipt. Join u
