 gto.com/events/2026/04/10/original_image678fc680-f229-4af0-8e91-0a45784f47
 99.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Toronto’s 1st dedicated singles mixer for law\, finance\, he
 althcare professionals who value ambition & lifestyle alignment.\nConnect 
 with singles in law\, finance\, and healthcare who value both career and c
 ommitment.\nThe community loved that Toronto Dating Hub is always innovati
 ng and introduced the first industry-specific singles mixers which include
 d healthcare\, teachers\, and the recent law+finance one. By popular reque
 st\, we are combining to introduce a mixer dedicated for for professionals
  in legal\, financial\, and healthcare spaces. ⚖️💼🩺\nThis isn’
 t just another mixer. It’s designed for people who understand demanding 
 schedules\, high standards\, and the reality of building a serious career.
 \nIf you’ve ever thought:\n“I want someone who actually gets my lifest
 yle\,” this is your room.\nWe’ve intentionally brought together a mix 
 of professionals across these industries — so while you’ll share simil
 ar ambition and values\, you’ll still meet people outside your exact rol
 e.\nThe open mingling format allows you to connect naturally\, with light 
 facilitation to keep conversations flowing. Expect a welcoming vibe\, mean
 ingful interactions\, and a room full of like-minded singles.\nWhat to exp
 ect at our event:\nA dedicated and experienced event host\, emcee and dati
 ng coach - Andrea Lo\nIcebreakers and intros\nOpen mingling (no forced rot
 ations)\nNo match forms — connect organically by exchanging contact info
 \nEvent flow explained at the start so you feel comfortable\nSPECIAL NOTES
 :\nWe do not fact-check or ask for professional credentials. We rely on ho
 nesty to ensure a positive experience for all. If misrepresentation is dis
 covered\, we reserve the right to take appropriate action regarding future
  event access.\nSince this is a newer event format/audience\, gender ratio
 s may be more flexible. We’re using this event to learn and refine futur
 e experiences for this audience.\nFeeling nervous cause you've never been 
 to a singles event? Not sure what to say/ how to get noticed?\nSign up for
  a 30 min coaching session for a special promo price of $30 + HST to help 
 prepare you for the event and to better your chances to geting (more) matc
 hes. Email us at torontodatinghub@gmail.com to book this or add this optio
 n to your cart when you check out!\nOr add the "Mini Attendee Profile" opt
 ion to your cart. Want to know who's attending and get the 411 on them so 
 you can figure out who you want to spend more time with? i.e. age\, job ti
 tle\, criteria - info that attendees opted in to share.\nhttps://www.toron
 toeventhub.com/events
LOCATION:Goodman Pub and Kitchen
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/toronto-dating-hub-singles-mixer-for-law
 -finance-healthcare-professionals-toronto/
X-SOURCE:blogTO
END:VEVENT
