DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260501T230000
UID:blogto-232209@blogto.com
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://blogto-production2-baselayer-display.blo
 gto.com/events/2026/03/15/original_imagec3c292f7-2b10-4114-a168-3fc283553c
 c3.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Overview\nHorror cabaret featuring drag\, cirque\, live music\
 , tarot\, and curiosities. Hosted by Kami Van Halst. One wicked night at R
 evival.\nThe Sinner’s Cabaret: Halfway to Halloween Celebration\nStep in
 to a dark and decadent night of spectacle as The Sinner’s Cabaret return
 s to celebrate the halfway mark to Halloween. Hosted by "Heavy Metal Lady 
 Gaga"- Kami Van Halst\, this immersive cabaret blends drag\, cirque\, live
  music\, magic\, and theatrical performance into one unforgettable evening
 .\nLive Performances By:\nGrim Pierce & Alice Witchfire – Twisted sidesh
 ow spectacle featuring daring feats\, dark glamour\, and the strange delig
 hts of the circus underworld.\nChris Mayhew – Mind-bending magic and psy
 chological illusion that will leave you questioning what is real.\nSeyonce
 \, Anne Alien & Yovska – Electrifying drag performances ranging from dar
 k glamour and theatrical horror to surreal creature fantasy. In partnershi
 p with Messy Productions.\nFeaturing a special appearance by the Heavy Met
 al Ballerina\, where classical ballet collides with the intensity of heavy
  metal.\nExplore the Vendor Market\, visit the Tarot Reading Room (Ape Ale
 xander\, Candace Bell\, and Madame de Savoye)\, and capture the night at o
 ur photo ops\, including special appearances by Pennywise and Perriwinkle\
 , while strange and spectacular acts unfold throughout the evening.\nThis 
 event utilizes all three levels of Revival\, transforming the venue into a
  dark cabaret music hall experience. The evening is designed as a standing
 -room-only event\, allowing guests to move freely between performances\, i
 nstallations\, and vendors throughout the space.\nArtwork by Alexis Leonar
 d
LOCATION:Revival Event Venue
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/the-sinners-cabaret-toronto/
X-SOURCE:blogTO
END:VEVENT
