 xperience an unforgettable night of salsa — dinner\, dancing\, and live 
 music all under one roof!\nBook a table for dinner and dancing\, or arrive
  after 9 PM to head straight to the dance floor.\nEvening Schedule\n� 7:
 00 PM – Doors open for dinner and drinks\n� 9:00 PM – Salsa lesson w
 ith Oscar Naranjo (no partner needed!)\n� 10:00 PM – First live salsa 
 set\, with a second set at midnight\n� 11:00 PM – Keep the energy goin
 g with DJ Van Gogh spinning Top 40\, salsa\, and Latin hits\nAbout the Ban
 d\nCanadian Latin Award nominees SWA Salsa Orchestra fuse traditional sals
 a with the rhythms of hip-hop\, R&B\, and soul\, putting an urban twist on
