 rnal genius. The superb young Toronto pianist Vanessa Yu joins the ensembl
 e in one of the greatest concertos of all time\, Beethoven's noble Piano C
 oncerto No. 5\, the "Emperor". Music Director Nurhan Arman leads the orche
 stra in Dmitri Shostakovich's poignant and personal Chamber Symphony in C 
