SUMMARY:Toronto Film School Showcase - Behind the Screens
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260502T130000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260502T190000
UID:blogto-232758@blogto.com
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://blogto-production2-baselayer-display.blo
 gto.com/events/2026/03/26/original_image98c28011-4d70-410f-bda9-3c2b6135da
 e8.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Curious what it actually takes to work in film\, TV\, graphic 
 design\, or video games? Toronto Film School’s Behind the Screens event 
 gives you a rare look behind the curtain. Step into hands-on workshops\, g
 et up close with professional gear\, explore student work\, and see where 
 our alumni have taken their creative careers. Discover how ideas become re
 al projects – and how creative passion can grow into a career.\nWhat the
  day has in store for you:\n– TFS CINEMA – View a curated collection o
 f our finest student-produced films.\n– ACTING WORKSHOP – Experience t
 he atmosphere of a live film set as cameras roll and you take direction in
  real time.\n– EQUIPMENT DEMO – Get up close with Hollywood-level came
 ras\, lenses\, lighting and gear from Sony and other equipment partners\, 
 with guidance from our Equipment Room Manager.\n– SCREENWRITING LAB – 
 Break down story fundamentals and shape them into a sharp logline in an in
 teractive storytelling challenge.\n– GAMES DEN – Play student-created 
 video games\, challenge yourself on arcade machines\, and explore game des
 ign.\n– GRAPHIC DESIGN STUDIO – Explore visual storytelling\, experime
 nt with composition\, and bring a graphic concept to life in an interactiv
 e design activation.\n– MEET THE CREATIVES – In a speed-networking for
 mat\, meet TFS alumni\, ask your questions\, and gain practical insight in
 to building a creative career.\n– ADMISSIONS LOUNGE – Explore Toronto 
 Film School programs\, meet program directors\, and get personalized guida
 nce on applications\, portfolios\, and next steps toward your creative car
 eer.
LOCATION:Steam Whistle's Locomotive Hall
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/toronto-film-school-showcase-behind-the-
 screens-toronto-2/
X-SOURCE:blogTO
END:VEVENT
