 28.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Welcome to Spring Market 2026!\nCelebrate the magic of spring 
 at Spring Market 2026 — a vibrant\, family-friendly shopping experience 
 just in time for Mother’s Day! Join us on Sunday\, May 3rd from 11:00 AM
  to 4:00 PM at Artscape Wychwood Barns and step into a beautifully curated
  day filled with creativity\, connection\, and joyful spring energy.\nProd
 uced by Sweetpea & Rose\, this one-day market brings together an exception
 al lineup of local makers\, artisans\, and small businesses\, each offerin
 g thoughtfully crafted goods you won’t find anywhere else. From fresh fl
 orals and handcrafted jewellery to stylish fashion pieces\, home décor\, 
 artisanal treats\, and meaningful Mother’s Day gifts — every booth is 
 designed to inspire.\nBut this isn’t just a market — it’s an experie
 nce. Expect a lively\, feel-good atmosphere with music in the air\, beauti
 ful spaces to explore\, and plenty of moments worth capturing. Bring the w
 hole family and enjoy a relaxed day out where little ones are welcome\, la
 ughter is encouraged\, and there’s something for everyone to discover.\n
 Make it a full spring outing — sip on your favourite coffee\, stroll thr
 ough the barn\, connect with passionate creators\, and take your time find
 ing pieces that truly feel special.\nWhether you're planning the perfect M
 other’s Day surprise\, meeting friends for a fun day out\, or simply loo
 king for something fresh and inspiring to do this spring\, Spring Market 2
 026 is the place to be.\nCome for the shopping\, stay for the atmosphere\,
  and leave with something you love.\nLearn about the Vendors on www.sweetp
 eaandrose.ca/2026-spring-market
LOCATION:Wychwood Barn
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/2026-spring-market-toronto/
