BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Anga's Farm: Bonsai Workshop for Beginners
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260503T150000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260503T170000
UID:blogto-232395@blogto.com
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://blogto-production2-baselayer-display.blo
 gto.com/events/2026/03/19/original_image7b788d14-81b9-4439-818e-2c719eaf72
 5b.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Bonsai Styling Workshop: Create\, Pot\, Wire & Trim Your Own B
 onsai!\nHave you ever wanted to try repotting or wiring a Bonsai but didn
 ’t know where to start? Or maybe you're excited to create your very own 
 Bonsai tree from scratch? This hands-on workshop is perfect for beginners 
 and anyone eager to dive into the art of Bonsai care and styling!\nIn this
  interactive\, hands-on workshop\, you'll create your very own Bonsai from
  start to finish. You’ll begin with a young Bonsai plant and\, under the
  guidance of an experienced Bonsai practitioner\, you will:\nChoose your p
 lant: Select from two different Bonsai plant varieties (Juniper\, Ficus or
  Jade).\nPot your plant: Transplant your selected Bonsai into a beautiful 
 5" ceramic pot with a saucer\, using the proper Bonsai soil.\nWire your Bo
 nsai: Learn the technique of wiring your Bonsai to train it into the shape
  and style you desire\, helping it take on its signature sculptural form.\
 nTrim and shape: Gain hands-on experience trimming and shaping your Bonsai
  to promote health and achieve a balanced aesthetic.\nYou will leave the w
 orkshop with your very own styled Bonsai tree in a decorative ceramic pot\
 , equipped with all the skills to continue nurturing and styling it at hom
 e.\nThe workshop is designed to give you practical\, hands-on experience\,
  working with the tools and techniques required to care for and shape your
  Bonsai from scratch. All materials and tools are provided\, including a 5
 " ceramic pot with saucer\, Bonsai soil\, wiring tools\, and your plant.\n
 Visit our website for more details & to sign up! www.angasfarm.ca
LOCATION:Anga's Farm & Nursery
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/angas-farm-bonsai-workshop-for-beginners
 -toronto-3/
X-SOURCE:blogTO
END:VEVENT
