 d7.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Art of the Pivot is an inspiring panel hosted by Shantelle Bis
 son\, best-selling author and founder of Without Losing Your Cool. The eve
 nt features a dynamic conversation moderated by Taylor Buckley\, founder o
 f Golden Hour Collective\, with Jordana H. Goldlist\, entrepreneur and bus
 iness strategist\, and Emily O’Brien\, entrepreneur and founder of Comeb
 ack Snacks. Together\, they will share powerful personal stories of overco
 ming significant life challenges and using those experiences as catalysts 
 for meaningful change. From navigating personal adversity to rebuilding ca
 reers and redefining purpose\, the conversation explores how life’s most
  difficult moments can spark unexpected opportunity and growth.\nGuests ar
 e invited to stay after the panel to mingle\, continue the conversation\, 
 and connect with a community of inspiring women who are embracing reinvent
 ion on their own terms. All proceeds support Elizabeth Fry Toronto.\nTicke
 ts are $25 and available at shantellebisson.com.
