 o seeking out and sharing "awesome coffee" with the community. With decade
 s of industry experience\, Momiji is a recognized leader in the Canadian c
 offee scene:\n- Owner/Operator at Hotblack Coffee\n- Head Roaster at Provi
 ncial Coffee Roasters\n- Two-Time Canadian Regional Barista Champion\n- Ex
 pert Judge for the Canadian National Brewers Cup and Canadian Aeropress Ch
 ampionship\n- Follow her journey: https://instagram.com/kishimomiji/ | htt
 ps://instagram.com/brewing_momi\nWorkshop Series\nComplete your coffee lea
 rning with our other sessions:\n- Coffee Cupping Session: March 1\, June7\
 , October 4\nhttps://coffee-cupping.eventbrite.com\n- Pour-Over Coffee Sem
 inar: March 29\nhttps://pour-over-coffee-seminar.eventbrite.com\nCancellat
 ion Policy\nWe understand plans change. Please note our refund tiers:\n- 8
