 g weekend. Sessions will resume on May 25th.)\nTime: 6:00 PM – 7:30 PM\n
 Location: Online via Zoom\nWeek 1: Free Flow Art: “Releasing Control”\
 nPurpose: Letting go of structure and perfection. Through intuitive\, body
 -led art-making\, you’ll explore what happens when you allow your hand t
 o move freely without overthinking.\nWeek 2: Non-Dominant Hand Drawing or 
 Bilateral Hand Drawing: “Accessing the Unconscious”\nPurpose: Using yo
 ur non-dominant hand or both hands together\,  to gently bypass the logica
 l mind and access deeper emotional layers.\nWeek 3: Symbolic Drawing: “M
 aking Meaning of What We Hold”\nPurpose: Gaining insight\, understanding
  patterns\, connecting with your inner narrative.\nWeek 4: Transformationa
 l Drawing: “Becoming”\nPurpose: Integration\, emotional shift\, steppi
 ng into a more open and flowing version of yourself. Link with Week 3.
