 gto.com/events/2026/04/09/original_image79eb5840-b1a4-4e9d-bd97-842c274754
 a6.jpg
DESCRIPTION:This Mother’s Day weekend\, Toronto-based artist Jilly Franc
 es unveils Like a Mirror\, Like a Mother\, Like a Memory\, a deeply person
 al exhibition bringing together three bodies of work\, Sky\, Rain\, and Gr
 ound\,  a poetic collaboration that traces the emotional landscape of moth
 erhood\, attention\, and the passing of time.\nArtist: Jilly Frances\nDate
 s: On view May 8–10\, 2026\nHours: 12–5 PM Friday\, 10-3 PM Saturday a
 nd Sunday. Visitors are invited to experience the skies in person and to f
 ind those that hold meaning for them. Attendance is free\, and all ages ar
 e welcome.
LOCATION:Kikospace
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/exhibition-like-a-mirror-like-a-mother-l
 ike-a-memory-toronto/
