BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Snow White On Ice
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260508T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260508T220000
UID:blogto-229956@blogto.com
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://blogto-production2-baselayer-display.blo
 gto.com/events/2026/01/28/original_image3dd87f6c-2dde-4a54-8360-8546d146ec
 f8.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Toronto is set for a spellbinding weekend this spring as Snow 
 White on Ice arrives for a limited engagement from May 8-10\, 2026. Presen
 ted by the world-renowned International Ice Stars\, this acclaimed product
 ion transforms the beloved fairytale into a breathtaking fusion of theatre
 \, elite figure skating\, and immersive stage design — all performed on 
 real ice.\nBrimming with charm and heart\, Snow White on Ice retells the c
 lassic story through expressive\, emotionally rich skating and striking vi
 sual detail. The Wicked Queen\, the Enchanted Mirror\, and the iconic red 
 apple set the scene for a journey filled with adventure\, friendship\, cou
 rage\, and hope.\nSnow White’s path through the forest introduces a live
 ly\, big-hearted group of companions who bring humour\, warmth\, and energ
 y to her story. Their kindness offsets the Queen’s mischief\, while the 
 arrival of a brave prince pulls the tale toward a joyful\, uplifting final
 e that audiences of all ages will love.\nLavishly staged and visually capt
 ivating\, Snow White on Ice blends elegance\, fun\, and theatrical flair i
 nto a family experience that resonates across generations. With one of the
  world’s most recognisable titles\, the show delivers universal family a
 ppeal and a level of storytelling rarely seen on ice.\nMay 8 - 10\nMeridia
 n Hall\, Toronto\nFriday\, May 8\, 2026: 7:30 pm\nSaturday\, May 9\, 2026:
  11 am\, 2:30 pm & 7:30 pm\nSunday\, May 10\, 2026: 11 am\, 2:30 pm & 7:30
  pm
LOCATION:Meridian Hall
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/snow-white-on-ice-toronto/
X-SOURCE:blogTO
END:VEVENT
