 f2.jpg
DESCRIPTION:The Women in PR North America WorkWell Conference in Toronto o
 n May 8\, 2026 brings together leaders in public relations\, investor rela
 tions\, communications\, media\, marketing\, and business for a day of con
 nection and inspiration during Women’s Health Month.\nDesigned for profe
 ssionals navigating today’s rapidly evolving communications landscape\, 
 the conference explores what it truly means to lead well\, strategically\,
  creatively\, and sustainably. Through expert-led panel discussions\, atte
 ndees will gain insights into what’s working now in communications\, how
  AI is transforming the industry\, building trust through visibility and c
 reator partnerships\, prioritizing wellbeing and ethical leadership\, and 
 creating profitable\, sustainable businesses.\nThroughout the day\, partic
 ipants will connect with industry leaders\, exchange ideas with peers from
  across North America\, and leave with practical strategies and meaningful
  relationships that support their next level of growth.\nWho should attend
 :\nPublic relations\, investor relations\, communications\, marketing\, bu
 siness\, and media professionals at all career stages who want to grow the
 ir leadership\, expand their network\, and stay ahead of the future of com
 munications.
LOCATION:Hart House Toronto
