 1b.jpg
DESCRIPTION:The Gluten-Free Bazaar returns for its third edition on May 9t
 h\, from 10 AM to 5 PM at Oakville Place Mall\, bringing together a vibran
 t and growing gluten-free community for a full day of discovery\, connecti
 on\, and support.\nIn collaboration with Oakville Place\, this year’s ba
 zaar will feature over 30 vendors offering a wide range of gluten-free pro
 ducts\, from baked goods and specialty foods to lifestyle brands and servi
 ces. Attendees can enjoy sampling\, shopping\, and exploring new and trust
 ed gluten-free options all in one place.\nBeyond shopping\, the event also
  highlights the importance of education and wellness within the gluten-fre
 e space. Community organizations and health-focused groups will be present
  to share valuable resources\, information\, and support for individuals a
 nd families navigating gluten-free living.\nWith an incredible turnout in 
 previous years\, the Gluten-Free Bazaar continues to grow as a welcoming a
 nd inclusive space that celebrates health\, local businesses\, and communi
 ty connection.
