BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Goodbye To The People I Used To Be An immersive self-portrait expe
 rience: guided by Rage Flowers Presented by Re-Work
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260509T130000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260509T170000
UID:blogto-233044@blogto.com
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://blogto-production2-baselayer-display.blo
 gto.com/events/2026/04/02/original_image0871ba13-175d-4f45-8f70-7c5f47b780
 1a.jpg
DESCRIPTION:​Goodbye To The People I Used To Be An immersive self-portra
 it experience — guided by Rage Flowers Presented by Re-Work\n​About Th
 is Experience\n​Goodbye To The People I Used To Be is a 4-hour immersive
  art experience that weaves together visualization\, deep personal reflect
 ion\, mirror work\, guided self-portraiture\, and rich communal exchange. 
 This is a space for people leaning into change\, those who want to face tr
 ansition and transformation with alignment and courage.\n​Through self-p
 ortraiture making\, you'll acknowledge and release the parts of yourself y
 ou've outgrown\, and create space for what's calling you forward.\n​We'r
 e not here to make perfect art\, there's no such thing. Your mark-making b
 ecomes a portal: to honest expression\, deep connection\, and closure.\n
 ​Expect play\, deep moments with yourself\, great snacks\, bright colour
 s\, maybe some joy\, tears\, and a lot of self-discovery.\n​Join us. Thi
 s is an intimate experience. Spots are limited. ✨
LOCATION:New Systems
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/goodbye-to-the-people-i-used-to-be-an-im
 mersive-self-portrait-experience-guided-by-rage-flowers-presented-by-re-wo
 rk-toronto/
