 57.jpg
DESCRIPTION:This Mother’s Day\, give mom the gift of peace of mind. SHN 
 is holding a Breast Health Screening Pop-up Day for community members. Whe
 ther you’re a mother or not\, we welcome everyone to this important day 
 of breast health screening.\nOntarians aged 40-49 can now self-refer for m
 ammograms\, making it easier to find and access information and services t
 hat support breast health. Screening helps people understand their health 
 and make informed decisions about their care\, supporting earlier detectio
 n of breast cancer. Regular mammograms save lives by identifying changes e
 arly\, when treatment is often more effective and outcomes are improved.\n
 Featuring:\nMammography screening (provided by female healthcare professio
 nals)\nGiveaways\nTreats and refreshments\nEducation and consult with brea
 st imaging navigators\nSchedule a mammogram for May 9 through one of these
  phone lines:\n416-438-2911\, ext. 88449\n416-284-8131\, ext. 64883
LOCATION:SHN General Hospital - CIBC Breast Health Clinic (Northpine DI De
 partment\, basement floor)
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/mothers-day-breast-health-screening-pop-
 up-toronto/
