 gto.com/events/2025/12/02/original_image0c1c0474-b582-4ee9-b1b8-b6c5bc5289
 50.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Relive the 2014 Academy Award® winning film\, Whiplash\, star
 ring Miles Teller and JK Simmons\, written and directed by Damien Chazelle
 \, in a mesmerizing live concert experience.\nWhiplash tells the story of 
 an ambitious young drummer Andrew studying at an elite conservatory\, and 
 his ruthless instructor Fletcher who pushes Andrew to the brink in the pur
 suit of greatness. ​\nThe show features a 18-piece jazz big band\, inclu
 ding a world-class drummer who travels with the show. Experience the great
  music and thrilling drum solos performed live along with the film!
LOCATION:Queen Elizabeth Theatre
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/whiplash-in-concert-toronto-2/
X-SOURCE:blogTO
END:VEVENT
