 f our usual first Monday show\, we have been invited by The Duke to perfor
 m on Sunday\, May 10th from 5:00 to 7:30 pm for a special Mother's Day cel
 ebration. We are so excited to bring you all kinds of great tunes that are
  (or were) our mothers' favourites! We are even taking requests from those
  of you who book ahead and let us know early (we will try our best to play
  them if they are in our repertoire...)!\nFor this occasion\, The Duke is 
 offering a lovely Prix Fix menu you can enjoy\, including choice of appeti
 zer\, entree and dessert (or you can stick with the menu a la carte). Get 
 your tickets early by using this link:\nhttps://www.eventbrite.ca/e/mother
 s-day-special-dinnershow-with-advocats-big-band-tickets-1985341557041.\n$2
 0 cash cover at the door (call 416-466-2624 to reserve). All entry proceed
 s go to the band. Treat the mothers in your life to a delightful evening!\
 nwww.advocatsbigband.com
LOCATION:The Duke
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/advocats-big-band-celebrates-mothers-day
 -at-the-duke-toronto-toronto/
