 gto.com/events/2026/03/29/original_imagedd4c0a5c-a9e0-4f08-9732-bc83d8affb
 2f.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Hosted by Zachary Hourihane (Swiftologist) and Madeline Rubica
 m (The Lizard Review)\, Evolution of a Snake is the hit podcast known for 
 its sharp\, analytical — and often hilarious — dissections of Taylor S
 wift’s career.\nIn The Showgirl Experience\, the duo turns their signatu
 re wit and cultural commentary toward one of Swift’s most controversial 
 albums in recent memory\, finally saying the things they’ve held back...
 until now.\nWith 100\,000 weekly listeners and a global fanbase\, Evolutio
 n of a Snake returns to the stage following sold-out shows across the U.S.
 \, U.K.\, Ireland\, and Australia. Expect deep dives\, hot takes\, and the
  kind of pop analysis you won’t hear anywhere else.\nTickets available @
  https://eventschaser.com/tickets/Evolution-of-a-Snake-The-Showgirl-Experi
 ence-The-Royal-Theatre---Toronto-Toronto-ON/7813222/
LOCATION:The Royal Theatre
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/evolution-of-a-snake-the-showgirl-experi
 ence-toronto/
X-SOURCE:blogTO
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Free Mothers Day Prenatal Pilates
