 gto.com/events/2026/03/12/original_image887b6fbc-c980-46fa-90f7-ecc3eb9911
 7b.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Free Mothers Day Prenatal Pilates\nSupport Your Strength. Hono
 ur Your Changing Body.\nThis Mother’s Day\, join us for a complimentary 
 Prenatal Pilates class at kaer Wellness. Created to support you through pr
 egnancy with intention and care. Move alongside other expectant mothers in
  a calm\, connected space designed to help you feel strong\, stable\, and 
 supported in every stage.\nThis class focuses on deep core activation\, pe
 lvic floor awareness\, posture\, and breath-led movement. Each exercise is
  thoughtfully guided to build strength and stability while respecting the 
 changes happening within your body.\nWhat to Expect:\nBreath & Connection:
  Gentle breathwork to support core function and create space for your grow
 ing baby.\nTargeted Strength: Controlled\, low-impact movements to strengt
 hen glutes\, back\, hips\, and deep abdominal muscles.\nMobility & Release
 : Stretching and alignment work to ease tension and improve posture.\nThis
  is your time to slow down\, tune in\, and build strength in a way that fe
 els steady and supportive.\nPlease note: This class is designed specifical
 ly for prenatal clients. Infants and children cannot be accommodated.
LOCATION:kaer wellness
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/free-mothers-day-prenatal-pilates-toront
 o/
X-SOURCE:blogTO
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Free Mothers Day Strength Class
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260510T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260510T100000
UID:blogto-232112@blogto.com
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://blogto-production2-baselayer-display.blo
 gto.com/events/2026/03/12/original_image64598039-29d2-47ec-bf55-79196ff7b6
 07.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Mother’s Day Strength\nStronger Together.\nThis Mother’s D
 ay\, join us at kaer Wellness for a complimentary strength class designed 
 to bring mothers and grandmothers together in movement. Whether you're bui
 lding strength\, maintaining it\, or returning to it\, this special editio
 n class is an opportunity to train side by side and celebrate the power of
  strong women across generations.\nRooted in functional strength and mobil
 ity\, this class focuses on movements that support you in everyday life—
 lifting\, carrying\, reaching\, and moving with confidence. Using weights\
 , bodyweight exercises\, and resistance bands\, you’ll build balanced st
 rength\, stability\, and endurance in a supportive\, high-energy environme
 nt.\nWhat to Expect:\nWarm-Up & Mobility: Dynamic movements to activate yo
 ur muscles and prepare your body for strength work.\nStrength Training: Fo
 undational exercises like squats\, rows\, and lunges layered with resistan
 ce to challenge and empower you.\nCool-Down & Recovery: Guided stretches t
 o restore flexibility and leave you feeling grounded and strong.\nCome mov
 e with us. Celebrate strength—in your body\, and in each other.\nPlease 
 note: Infants and children cannot be accommodated during this class. Clien
 ts with a baby are welcome to attend a Strength with Baby class instead.
LOCATION:kaer wellness
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/free-mothers-day-strength-class-toronto/
X-SOURCE:blogTO
END:VEVENT
