BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tune In Tuesday: Monthly Sound & Relaxation Therapy Workshop
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260512T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260512T210000
UID:blogto-232649@blogto.com
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://blogto-production2-baselayer-display.blo
 gto.com/events/2026/03/24/original_imagedb8abb0c-e28c-47b1-8fa1-b03e041567
 cb.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Tune In Tuesday: Monthly Sound + Relaxation Therapy Workshop\n
 *Sessions are eligible for health insurance coverage under Psychotherapy S
 ervices*\nTUNE IN TUESDAY is a monthly sound bath and vocal toning relaxat
 ion therapy workshop that invites you to “tune in” to deep relaxation\
 , inner stillness\, and self-reflection.\nSettle into your week with sooth
 ing sound vibrations\, gentle vocal toning practices and learn about how i
 ntegrating sound and vibration into your everyday life can help you reduce
  stress\, restore energetic balance\, and cultivate contentment.\nJoin for
  one session or many! No experience required.\n• When: Tuesdays - May 12
 th and June 23rd\n• Time: 7:30 p.m. - 9:00 p.m.\n• Venue: Grateful Den
  (390 Dupont Street\, Suite 201\, Toronto)\n• Accessibility Notice: Taki
 ng one flight of stairs is required to access the studio space. There is n
 o elevator in the building.
LOCATION:Grateful Den
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/tune-in-tuesday-monthly-sound-relaxation
 -therapy-workshop-toronto/
X-SOURCE:blogTO
END:VEVENT
