 e comprehensive\, evidence-based education designed to prepare you to begi
 n supporting women and families with clarity and confidence.\nYou will lea
 ve grounded in the role of the doula.\nSkilled in foundational support tec
 hniques.\nReady to take your next steps toward certification and practice.
 \nYour Registration Includes\n- 20 hours of live\, instructor-led online t
 raining\n- A comprehensive digital DONA Birth Doula Training Manual\n- An 
