BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Wine Fest Toronto: Spring 2026
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260515T170000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260515T220000
UID:blogto-233216@blogto.com
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://blogto-production2-baselayer-display.blo
 gto.com/events/2026/04/06/original_imagebec8d47e-6a2a-4359-9c87-093a4773a8
 a6.jpg
DESCRIPTION:The city’s favourite wine and drinks festival returns this M
 ay long weekend to Toronto’s iconic Heritage Court in the Enercare Centr
 e!\nThe multi-day festival invites guests to explore\, sip\, and discover 
 at their own pace\, with fascinating wines and drinks from around the worl
 d\, shorter lines\, and a more elevated tasting experience designed for bo
 th seasoned wine and drink lovers and curious newcomers\, all in one place
 .\nTo complement guests’ tasting journey\, Wine Fest will feature music\
 , artisanal food truck eats\, and photo moments throughout the festival. T
 he popular seminar sessions also return\, offering complimentary classes w
 ith admission\, allowing guests to expand their beverage knowledge.\nWine 
 Fest Toronto is also introducing a flexible token system\, allowing guests
  to browse the full drinks list in advance\, plan their tastings through a
