 xperience.\n‘The French Experience\,’ Powered by Taste France\, also m
 akes its debut this spring\, offering guests a rare opportunity to experie
 nce the diversity of France’s winemaking traditions.\nA world of wine an
 d drinks awaits!\nDate & Time:\nFriday\, May 15th\, 5:00 PM-10:00 PM\nSatu
 rday\, May 16th\, 1:00 PM-10:00 PM\,\nSunday\, May 17th\, 1:00 PM-9:00 PM
