 54.jpg
DESCRIPTION:MRG Live presents one of the most critically hailed comedians 
 of his generation. Alex Edelman is best known for solo shows that blur the
  line between his stand-up comedy roots and narrative-driven storytelling.
  His last offering\, Just for Us\, played more than 500 performances all o
 ver the world\, including Broadway\, before premiering as an HBO original 
 comedy special in April 2024\, earning him a place on the Time 100 list an
 d both a Tony and Emmy award. Edelman appeared in Jerry Seinfeld’s direc
 torial debut for Netflix\, Unfrosted. He will next be seen starring in The
  Paper\, Greg Daniels’s The Office spinoff for Peacock. Edelman is also 
 a writer and consulting producer for the show.\nTickets: https://www.ticke
