 gto.com/events/2026/04/09/original_image679753d5-5fd7-49b8-80ed-2fdd250814
 89.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Glow in the Vines is an immersive wellness and culinary experi
 ence set among the vineyards\, bringing together movement\, inspiring spea
 kers\, workshops\, wine\, music\, food\, and meaningful conversation — d
 esigned to create moments of pause\, joy\, and connection.\n🌿 Guided We
 llness Journey\nMovement\, meditation\, and breathwork accompanied by acou
 stic guitar designed to restore and energize.\n🎶 Live Music & DJ\nSoulf
 ul\, inspiring live performances paired with an all-afternoon DJ set to en
 ergize the vineyard atmosphere.\n✨ Inspiring Speakers\nThoughtful voices
  sharing stories and insights to spark reflection\, connection\, and inspi
 ration.   Featuring Sara Westbrook and Tonia Jahshan\, each bringing their
  own unique approach to emotional well-being\, ritual\, and personal growt
 h.\n🌸 Interactive Workshops & Sensory Activations\nEngaging experiences
  designed to awaken creativity and curiosity.  Explore offerings such as d
 ot mandala painting\, calligraphy workshops\, wine tastings\, and glow-ins
 pired photo moments.\n🍷 Private Château des Charmes Winery Tour & Inti
 mate Tasting\nDiscover the story and flavours behind one of Niagara’s ic
 onic wineries.\n🍽 Gourmet Vineyard Lunch\nA beautifully curated lunch w
 ith sparkling wine and botanical mocktails.\n🎁 Exclusive Glow Gift\nA t
 houghtfully curated take-home gift\n✨ Giving Back\nAn opportunity to sup
 port Niagara Health Foundation through a special on-site activation\n🏨 
 Luxury Hotel Stay Packages Available\nExtend your Glow experience and enjo
 y preferred access to beautiful accommodations at Vintage Hotels.
