 gto.com/events/2026/04/09/original_image91a100ff-cbf1-4f01-896e-cb8d321b5c
 1f.jpg
DESCRIPTION:The Yacht Rock Show sails into the iconic El Mocambo\, Toronto
 !\nThe Yacht Rock Show Canada is an authentic tribute to the 70s & 80s Cla
 ssic Smooth Rock Era that defined a generation. Experience an unforgettabl
 e musical voyage at this Yacht Rock themed party. The Yacht Rock Show perf
 orms classic hits from artists including: Toto\, Styx\, The Doobie Brother
 s\, Michael McDonald\, Christopher Cross\, Kenny Loggins\, Steely Dan\, Bo
 z Scaggs\, Player\, Little River Band\, Ambrosia.\nSupporting the event wi
 ll be DJ JChameleon who will be DJing rare & classic yacht rock before\, a
 fter and in between sets. A trained guitarist\, DJ\, and music educator JC
 hameleon (real name Josh Laing) is foremost a preservationist\, collecting
  classic and rare cuts in lossless fidelity. Josh has been performing and 
 promoting events in Toronto and the Northeast US since 2005 and has been h
 osting the Harbour Nights live to air DJ show and live events since 2020 a
 nd was the first person to throw a yacht rock DJ parety in Toronto back in
  2007.\nNeon Palms Room. Doors at 7:00 p.m.
LOCATION:El Mocambo
