BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:The Yacht Rock Show @ The El Mocambo
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260516T200000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260516T223000
UID:blogto-232229@blogto.com
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://blogto-production2-baselayer-display.blo
 gto.com/events/2026/03/16/original_imageb233a734-f306-496b-8d7e-c4983cc786
 5c.jpg
DESCRIPTION:May 16\, 2026\nThe Yacht Rock Show performs at the iconic El M
 ocambo for Toronto's First Annual Yacht Rock Celebration\nPowered by MUSI
 CMIX.CA\nTORONTO—ONE NIGHT ONLY\; The Yacht Rock Show is Canada's origin
 al authentic tribute to the 70s & 80s Classic Smooth Rock Era that defined
  a generation. Join us for an unforgettable musical voyage at this Yacht 
 Rock themed party—dance\, listen\, and experience note-perfect\, interac
 tive performances of classic hits from artists including Toto\, Styx\, The
  Doobie Brothers\, Michael McDonald\, Christopher Cross\, Kenny Loggins\, 
 Steely Dan\, Boz Scaggs\, Gerry Rafferty\, Player\, Little River Band\, Am
 brosia and more.\nThis is a must-see if you’re a yacht rock fan. Special
  guest DJ @jchameleon will be spinning the coolest Yacht Deep Cuts all nig
 ht.\n\nThe El Mocambo is a legendary live music and entertainment venue in
  Toronto\, Canada\, that has hosted countless world-famous artists since i
 t opened in 1948\, including The Rolling Stones\, Elvis Costello\, Blondie
 \, The Ramones\, and Stevie Ray Vaughan. The new El Mocambo features state
 -of-the-art sound and lighting\, a recording studio\, and multiple floors 
 for events and performances\, offering a modern\, VIP live music experienc
 e while maintaining its historical significance.\nDon't miss this nostalgi
 c experience—wear your favourite Yacht Rock fashion!\nThe El Mocambo is 
 fully accessible for people of all abilities.\nThe Yacht Rock Show welcom
 es everyone! "Love is love\, and all are welcome"\nEvent Date: May 16\, 20
 26\nEvent Time: 8:00pm\nVenue Page: https://elmocambo.com/event/the-yacht
 -rock-show/\nTickets: https://buy.pressplaytickets.com/yrs-elmo/
LOCATION:The El Mocambo
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/the-yacht-rock-show-the-el-mocambo-toron
 to/
