 e classics"\nSunday May 17\, 2026\nBreak For LOVE returns for our Victoria
  Day Sunday edition!\nDJ Kenny Glasgow\nDJ Dave Campbell\nDJ Yogi\nhosted 
 by:\nPedro HotStepper\nTickets: https://bfl-may17.eventbrite.ca\nPortland 
 Room\, 2nd floor\, 600 King St W\, Toronto. Doors: 10PM\nBreak For LOVE re
 turns with another unforgettable night dedicated to house music and rare g
 roove classics — this time in a brand new space we’re excited to share
  with you.\nWe’re taking things to Portland Room\, a loft-style venue in
  the heart of downtown Toronto\, bringing an intimate vibe with an outstan
 ding sound system that’s built for the full Break For LOVE experience. E
 xpect deep grooves\, soulful energy\, and that signature dancefloor connec
 tion from start to finish.\nHeadlining the night is special guest DJ Kenny
  Glasgow — a true pioneer of Toronto’s house music scene and a foundat
 ional figure in shaping its sound and culture. Known for his deep\, drivin
 g sets and global reputation\, Kenny brings a level of experience and ener
 gy that perfectly aligns with the Break For LOVE vibe.\nHappening on Victo
 ria Day long weekend Sunday night — the perfect excuse to lose yourself 
