 e9.jpg
DESCRIPTION:The authentic atmosphere of a Rio baile comes to Canada with e
 xplosive beats\, contagious dance energy with special guest direct from Ri
 o!\nSHOW DETAILS\n9:00 PM - Doors open\n10:00 PM - Show begins\n$40 ADVANC
 E + FEES + HST = $49.72\nTICKETS ARE GENERAL ADMISSION AND DO NOT GUARANTE
 E SEATING.\nLulaworld Festival (May 11 to 17)\nJoin us at Lula Lounge to c
 elebrate the 20th annual Lulaworld festival\, marking two decades of local
  and international jazz\, Latin\, Brazilian\, soul and folk from around th
 e globe and around the corner.\nEU AMO BAILE FUNK – Rio to Canada Editio
 n\nTati Quebra-Barraco\,\nDirect from the vibrant streets of Rio de Janeir
 o\, Eu Amo Baile Funk lands in Canada for a night celebrating the raw ener
 gy and cultural power of Brazilian funk. Born in Rio’s iconic dance part
 ies\, Baile Funk is more than music — it’s a movement\, a rhythm\, and
  a powerful expression of Brazilian urban culture.\nThis special edition b
 rings the authentic atmosphere of a Rio baile to the Canadian stage\, with
  explosive beats\, contagious dance energy\, and an immersive party experi
 ence that invites everyone to move.\nHeadlining the night is legendary Bra
 zilian funk icon Tati Quebra-Barraco\, one of the most influential voices 
 in the history of funk carioca. Known for her bold lyrics and groundbreaki
 ng presence in the scene\, Tati helped bring Baile Funk from the favelas o
 f Rio to the global stage.\nExpect a high-energy night of DJs\, dance\, an
 d the unmistakable sound of Funk Carioca\, connecting cultures and bringin
 g the spirit of Rio de Janeiro to Canada.\nGet ready for a night where the
  bass hits hard\, the dancefloor moves as one\, and the vibe is pure Rio
LOCATION:Lula Lounge
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/lulaworld-2026-eu-amo-baile-funk-tati-qu
 ebra-barraco-toronto/
