 gto.com/events/2026/04/09/original_imageb74450c7-dbb7-4d53-8690-3fcbba5654
 81.jpg
DESCRIPTION:One of Toronto’s favourite fundraising events is back! Marti
 ni Madness returns this May 2026\, presented by CIBC and The Andlauer Fami
 ly. The event brings together cocktail enthusiasts\, community leaders\, a
 nd supporters for an unforgettable evening in support of life-changing med
 ical research.\nIn support of the GEM Project through the Sinai Health Fou
 ndation\, Martini Madness raises critical funds to help uncover the causes
  of Crohn’s disease and ulcerative colitis—two chronic conditions affe
 cting more than 320\,000 Canadians.\nThe Toronto event will feature an ele
 vated\, all-inclusive experience\, where guests can enjoy unlimited signat
 ure martinis crafted by top mixologists\, curated food stations\, and a li
 vely atmosphere designed for connection and celebration. A premium raffle 
 will also offer exclusive items and experiences\, with all proceeds suppor
 ting research efforts that are changing lives.\nWith thousands of Canadian
 s diagnosed with inflammatory bowel disease each year—including massivel
 y increasing rates in children and young adults—the need for continued r
 esearch and innovation has never been more urgent.
LOCATION:Ricarda's
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/martini-madness-toronto/
X-SOURCE:blogTO
END:VEVENT
