 ada at the 2026 Air Guitar World Championships in Oulu\, Finland this Augu
 st 26-29th!\nAir Guitar is an expression of World Peace - When you are hol
 ding an Air Guitar\, you can’t be holding a gun! Air Guitar Canada is a 
