 6c.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate Asian Heritage Month: Support & shop local from Asia
 n vendors\, enjoy Asian food & drinks\, & cute photo opp for all! 1 day on
 ly!\nJoin Toronto Event Hub as we host our 3rd annual Asian Heritage Month
  Popup Market on May 24th at DZO Viet Eatery in Chinatown across the AGO.\
 nCome browse and see what treasures you'll find at our market - support & 
 shop from local Asian-owned businesses\, while enjoying amazing food and d
 rink options. We have giveaways\, live performance(s)\, and a unique photo
  experience\, and so much more.\nMake our market as a stop along your Door
 s Open Toronto tour route as we're right by OCAD and Nathan Phillips Squar
 e.\n***VENDOR APPLICATIONS are currently OPEN - only 10 spots in total! AP
 PLY NOW.*** Successful vendor referrals = extra marketing promotion on our
  online channels (50K exposure).\nWe are also looking for sponsors & cultu
 ral performances.\nFREE admission - everyone is welcome - this is a family
  (and dog)-friendly event.\nThis is a mostly indoor market as we're taking
  over the restaurant - it will happen rain or shine!\nYou have EXTRA chanc
 es to win sweet prizes if you check in to the event with your Eventbrite t
 icket & follow @torontoeventhub on Instagram / Facebook.\nhttps://www.toro
 ntoeventhub.com/events
