BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:2nd International Meet and Expo on Renewable and Sustainable Energ
 y
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260525T093000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260525T183000
UID:blogto-227867@blogto.com
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://blogto-production2-baselayer-display.blo
 gto.com/events/2025/12/06/original_image1d012990-a58d-4e9f-86eb-c74a11713e
 c8.jpg
DESCRIPTION:It is with great joy and enthusiasm that we extend a warm invi
 tation to participants from around the world to join us for the 2nd Intern
 ational Meet and Expo on Renewable and Sustainable Energy (RENEWABLEMEET20
 26)\, taking place in Rome\, Italy\, from May 25–26\, 2026.\nFollowing t
 he resounding success of RENEWABLEMEET2025\, held in Zurich\, Switzerland\
 , where we were honored to host a distinguished lineup of high-profile spe
 akers\, including leading professors\, CEOs\, researchers\, and industry e
 xperts\, we are thrilled to continue this journey with the next edition of
  the conference.\nThe theme for RENEWABLEMEET2026\, “Empowering a Greene
 r Future through Renewable and Sustainable Energy\,” aims to bring toget
 her visionaries\, innovators\, and scholars from across the globe. This co
 nference will provide a dynamic platform to explore groundbreaking researc
 h and emerging technologies through carefully curated scientific sessions 
 covering Renewable Energy\, Power Energy\, Electrical Energy\, and their r
 eal-world applications in industries\, research institutes\, electronic la
 boratories\, thermal energy plants\, and energy grids.\nThe future of rene
 wable and sustainable energy has never looked brighter. Don’t miss this 
 exceptional opportunity to connect\, collaborate\, and innovate with the g
 lobal energy community.\nWarm regards\,\nR. Shashika\nConference Manager\n
 Organizing Committee\nRENEWABLEMEET2026
LOCATION:Rome\, Italy
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/2nd-international-meet-and-expo-on-renew
 able-and-sustainable-energy-toronto/
X-SOURCE:blogTO
END:VEVENT
