BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:THE SOVEREIGN GALA: GENESIS - Toronto Tech Week's Biggest Event! -
  Black Tie\, Masquerade Networking Social/Mixer
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260527T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260527T230000
UID:blogto-232481@blogto.com
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://blogto-production2-baselayer-display.blo
 gto.com/events/2026/03/21/original_image84019e19-27ec-43a2-9744-fd3ad8b07a
 ab.jpg
DESCRIPTION:About the Event\nTHE SOVEREIGN GALA: GENESIS is not your typic
 al Toronto networking event. This will be the most prestigious event of To
 ronto Tech Week! Prepare for an evening of elegance\, mystery\, and powerf
 ul connections with entrepreneurs\, investors\, founders\, and influential
  leaders.\nWe are Proud to be an Official Partner of Toronto Tech Week.\nS
 et in a luxurious black-tie atmosphere\, this masquerade blends elegance w
 ith connection. A selection of Gourmet food\, and an Open Bar to share con
 versations. Behind the masks\, guests you will meet include some of the mo
 st ambitious minds across Tech\, AI\, Real Estate\, Venture Capital\, and 
 Startups. Expect a refined social environment where meaningful conversatio
 ns\, partnerships\, and new ideas can emerge naturally.\nWhat To Expect\n
 🍽️ Food Experience\nEnjoy elevated food stations throughout the night
 :\n• Oven-Baked Custom Pizza Station – Fresh pizzas made to order• C
 hef-Curated Gourmet Bites served throughout the evening• Artisan Gelato 
 Station with premium flavors• Delicious small plates perfect for minglin
 g and socializing\n🍸 Drinks & Bar\nA premium bar experience designed fo
 r the night:\n• Signature Masquerade Cocktails crafted exclusively for t
 he event• Open Bar with premium spirits\, wine\, and beer• Drinks cura
 ted by professional mixologists\n🎭 Black & Gold Masquerade\nEnter a stu
 nning black-and-gold themed venue where masks and black-tie attire create 
 an atmosphere of elegance and intrigue.The masquerade setting adds mystery
  while making conversations more relaxed and memorable.\n💎 GEMSTONE FIN
 ANCE PRESENTS\n💍 An Exclusive Gemstone Auction\nBrowse and bid in a sil
 ent gemstone auction. featuring a limited collection of unique certified p
 recious gems from the Gemstone Finance vaults. Timeless beauty and value p
 resented in a curated gemstone browsing experience\, and at the end of the
  night\, they can be yours forever. We will be announcing more specifics a
 s we draw closer to the Gala.\n🎟️ WIN a Precious Gemstone\nEvery atte
 ndee will also be entered into a draw to win a Certified Precious Gemstone
  with an appraised value of over $1000! Details to be announced.\n🥂 Lux
 ury Social Atmosphere\nExpect a vibrant environment with great music by by
  Rotation Sensation\, great people\, and meaningful conversations\, all de
 signed to spark new ideas\, partnerships\, and opportunities.\n🚐 Luxury
  Limo Shuttle/Party Bus\nFor a seamless experience\, complimentary limo sh
 uttles will run between Toronto and the venue throughout the night. (Detai
 ls will be shared with approved guests)\nItinerary\n7:00 PM – 7:30 PM | 
 Arrivals & Check-In\nGuests arrive\, check in\, and step into the black an
 d gold masquerade atmosphere.\nLuxury Limo Shuttle/Party Bus Downtown Toro
 nto Pickup Starts at 7:00pm (Details will be shared with approved guests)\
 n7:30 PM – 10:30 PM | Party & Social Experience\nEnjoy the best of Toron
 to Tech Week while enjoying music\, food\, the gemstones on display\, the 
 silent auction and open bar in an elegant setting.\n11:00 PM – 1:00 AM |
  Final Connections & Closing Moments\nExchange contacts\, continue convers
 ations\, and head out to the after parties! (Official Partner After Partie
 s TBD)\nJoin Us on WhatsApp\nBe part of our growing WhatsApp Community! Co
 ntinue the conversations\, share information\, and connect with our growin
 g community by clicking here.\nDress Code:\nAn evening of elegance and mys
 tery. Guests are expected to wear formal black tie attire paired with a ma
 squerade mask.\nGentlemen are expected to wear a tuxedo or black formal su
 it with bow tie.\nLadies are encouraged to wear evening gowns or elegant c
 ocktail dresses.\nMasquerade masks are highly encouraged to embrace the my
 stery and atmosphere of the evening.\nColors that complement the event aes
 thetic:Black\, white\, gold\, metallics\, and deep jewel tones.\n🔞 Age 
 Requirement: 19+\n“Toronto Tech Week is a citywide celebration of the pe
 ople building what’s next. From May 25–29\, 2026\, founders\, investor
 s\, and builders come together for hundreds of community-led events across
  Toronto\, connecting tens of thousands of people around Canadian tech. T
 orontotechweek.com.”\nEVENT SPONSOR:\nTriggerVox - Turn Your Calls and W
 ebsite Into aSales Machine. Acts as your 24/7 Receptionist (Scheduling\, Q
 &A\, Customer Support\, FAQ)\nTriggerVox talks to your leads within 30 sec
 onds\, answers questions\, handles objections\, and books appointments so 
 you never miss a sale/client/Customer!\nWhat to Bring\n✅ Your Mask & Bla
 ck Tie Attire✅ Business Cards or LinkedIn QR Code✅ Friends & Colleague
 s who would enjoy connecting with Toronto’s most ambitious community (Al
 l guests must sign up and be approved)
LOCATION:1377 The Queensway Unit 101\, Toronto\, ON M8Z 1T1
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/the-sovereign-gala-genesis-toronto-tech-
 weeks-biggest-event-black-tie-masquerade-networking-socialmixer-toronto/
X-SOURCE:blogTO
END:VEVENT
