ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://blogto-production2-baselayer-display.blo
 gto.com/events/2025/12/12/original_image9c0e6143-2dc6-4c2f-bf31-6e2bd539ff
 9b.jpg
DESCRIPTION:The 2nd World Summit on Smart Grid and Clean Energy Technologi
 es (WSSGCE-2026) is an international conference focused on advancing innov
 ations in smart grids\, renewable energy\, and sustainable power systems. 
 Held from June 10–12\, 2026\, in Prague\, Czech Republic\, the summit br
 ings together researchers\, engineers\, industry experts\, and policymaker
 s to exchange knowledge and discuss emerging technologies. Key themes incl
 ude intelligent power systems\, grid modernization\, energy storage\, clea
 n energy integration\, digitalization\, and electric mobility. All accepte
 d submissions will undergo rigorous peer review and be considered for inde
 xing in major scientific databases\, supporting global collaboration and p
 rogress in clean energy advancements.
LOCATION:The Prague Restaurant
