BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Designing the Movies: Dodsworth
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260611T184500
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260611T210000
UID:blogto-232861@blogto.com
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://blogto-production2-baselayer-display.blo
 gto.com/events/2026/03/30/original_image60bab9fb-b316-4b72-95e8-25c5af42bb
 05.jpg
DESCRIPTION:Noah Baumbach’s Marriage Story wishes it were this movie! Wi
 lliam Wyler’s 1936 masterpiece about a crumbling marriage follows the un
 happy middle-aged couple on the grand European vacation they’ve always d
 reamed of\, as they debate whether to make it work or move on with other p
 eople. the striking Art Deco and streamline sets earned Canadian productio
 n designer Richard Day the second of his seven Academy Awards for Best Art
  Direction. New 4K Restoration\, presented with an introduction by series 
 host Nathalie Atkinson. $18/$15
LOCATION:Revue Cinema
URL:https://www.blogto.com/events/designing-the-movies-dodsworth-toronto/
X-SOURCE:blogTO
END:VEVENT
